Ibi biganiro biba mu buryo bw'uko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kizaba kimeze.
Nanone kandi, hakomeje kugaragara ko hakenewe impinduka mu mirire, kandi ko iterambere ry'iyo virusi rifite ingaruka ku buremere bw'indwara.
Virusi za corona (CoVs) ni zo mu muryango wa coronaviridae ugizwe n'amatsinda y'imikorere ya virusi za RNA ziterwa n'umusemburo, ziterwa n'umusemburo w'ubushake, ziterwa n'umusemburo w'umwirondoro umwe.
Izo virusi, zifite ingirabuzima fatizo nini cyane z'imiterere iri hagati ya 26 na 32 mu virusi za RNA, zahawe izina rya "CoVs" kubera imiterere isa n'ikamba iri munsi ya mikorosikopi ya elegitoroniki.
Mu buryo bw'ibanze, za CoV zifite genomes zitagira ibice zifite imiterere imwe.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu by'imiterere y'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima (ORF1a na ORF1b) ni ibinyabuzima bibiri binini byisumbuyeho, bihindura pp1a na pp1ab.
Polyprotein ikomeza gutunganywa kugira ngo ibyaremwe bigere kuri 16 bita nsp1~16.
Mu gice gisigaye cy'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima, harimo spike (S), enveloppe (E), membrane (M) na nucleoproteins (N).
Hariho n'imikorere y'ibinyabuzima by'inyongera by'ubwoko butandukanye, bikoreshwa n'ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoV.
Bitewe n'ubundi buryo bwo gutandukanya ibigize poroteyine, CoVs zigabanywa mu miryango ine (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV), muri yo beta-CoV ni yo ifite HCoVs nyinshi kandi igagabanywa mu miryango ine (A, B, C na D).
Ibimenyetso by'ibanze byerekana ko udusimba n'ibinyamushongo aribyo bitanga umurongo wa alpha-CoVs na beta-CoVs, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zitanga umurongo w'ibanze wa gamma-CoVs na delta-CoVs.
Mu myaka ibihumbi, CoVs zakomeje kurenga inzitizi z'ubwoko kandi zigaragara nk'izindi ndwara z'ingenzi zibasira abantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana abantu barindwi bafite virusi ya HCoVs.
Muri byo harimo HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 alpha-CoVs.
Izindi beta-CoV eshanu zirimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 byibanze ku kugaragaza ibimenyetso byoroheje nk'ibicurane n'ibicurane.
Mu buryo bunyuranye, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 nshya, ni indwara zandura cyane, zitera indwara zikomeye z'ubuhumekero bwo hasi mu barwayi benshi cyane bafite indwara z'umuvuduko mwinshi w'ubuhumekero (ARDS) n'ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E, B814, bwavumbuwe mu myaka ya za 60 mu buryo bw'imvune zaturutse mu mazuru y'abarwayi ba colds.
Kuva icyo gihe, amakuru yindi yakusanyijwe n'ubushakashatsi bwimbitse ku byerekeye HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi byerekana ibimenyetso byigenga.
Mu by'ukuri, mbere y'uko SARS itangira, abantu benshi bemeraga ko ubwandu bwa HCoVs busanzwe butari bubi.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye mu mwaka wa 2003, cyibasiye abantu barenga 8000, ku kigero cy'abapfa ku kigero cya 10% gusa, kikaba ari kimwe mu byorezo byangije byinshi mu mateka y'iki gihe.
Hashize imyaka icumi, icyorezo cya MERS cyateye icyorezo gikomeje kwiyongera mu karere ka Arabiya, kigakwira hirya no hino ku isi.
2019 novel HCoV (2019-nCoV), nyuma yahawe izina rya SARS-CoV-2, ni yo ntandaro y'icyorezo cy'icyorezo cya Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19), kimaze guhitana abantu 3,120 na 91,000 bamaze kwandura kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Amatara y'umuburo aravuza, kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
HCoVs zose uko ari 7 zaturutse mu nyamaswa, haba mu nyamaswa z'ibinyamushongo, mu mpfizi cyangwa mu nyamaswa zo mu ngo.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi bishyigikira ko HCoVs zose zakomotse ku mikorobe, zikaba zifite virusi zinyuranye cyane n'izindi, kandi zidakora indwara, ariko zigaragaza itandukaniro rinini mu miterere y'ibinyabuzima.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateye ibibazo bikomeye mu buvuzi, mu bya siyansi, mu mibereho n'umuco mu Bushinwa no ku isi.
Gushakisha inkomoko y'inyamaswa ya HCoVs bitanga urufatiro rwo gusobanukirwa amateka y'ibanze, imbaraga zituma habaho guhungabanya ubwoko, n'impamvu zituma habaho guhungabana.
Ibi bishobora kuyobora cyangwa guhuza ubushakashatsi ku bimenyetso, ibinyampande n'ibyongereraho SARS-CoV-2 bifite ingaruka zikomeye mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'igihe kizaza.
Muri iyi mpapuro, dutanga isesengura ry'inkomoko y'inyamaswa, ikwirakwira ry'ubwoko n'ubwandu bwa HCoVs.
By'umwihariko, turashyira ahagaragara kandi tukaganira ku ngingo rusange ivuga ko virusi z'ibanze za HCoVs zidakunda gutera indwara mu byuma by'ingirabuzimafatizo zisanzwe, ariko ko zikunda gutera indwara nyuma yo kwanduzwa mu bwoko bushya.
Tuzasuzuma kandi uko HCoV igenda yiyongera, aho ubwandu bugenda bwiyongera, ariko indwara zikagenda zigabanuka.
Muri iyi gahunda, hatangazwa ingaruka z'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Amakuru y'uko hari hari za CoV z'inyamaswa yatangiye mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 30.
Mbere y'uko ubwoko bwa HCoV-229E bufatwa bwa mbere mu byuma by'amaso by'abarwayi ba cyanko, hari ubwoko bwinshi bwa CoVs zaturutse mu nyamaswa nyinshi zanduye, harimo inkoko, imbeba, inka, ingurube, imbwa n'injangwe.
HCoVs 7 nizo zavuzwe mu myaka icumi ishize.
Umwanzuro muto w'amateka y'igihe HCoV yavumbuwe (Igishushanyo cya 1) uzatanga amakuru kandi utange inyigisho.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E bwavumbuwe mu mwaka wa 1966 mu mibiri y'abarwayi bafite ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hejuru, nyuma y'aho buhindurwa mu mibiri y'ibihaha bya WI-38.
Mu barwayi banduye HCoV-229E, 10~20% by'abanduye bagaragaje ibimenyetso by'ibicurane birimo umutwe, gucika intege, guhumeka no kugira ubumuga bw'umugongo, hamwe n'ibicurane by'umuriro n'igisebe.
Nyuma mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 yahiswemo inzira yo mu bwonko bw'imbeba zinywa amata no mu buryo bwo gukwirakwiza ingingo.
Ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa HCoV-OC43 bisa n'ibyavuye ku bwandu bwa HCoV-229E, ariko ntibishobora gutandukanywa n'ubwandu bw'izindi virusi z'ubuhumekero nka influenza A na rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byombi byiganje ku isi hose kandi birashoboka ko byanduzwa cyane mu gihe cy'imbeho, aho ikirere kiba cyifashe neza.
Ubusanzwe, iyo virusi zombi zigira igihe cy'iterambere kitarenze icyumweru, nyuma y'icyo kigera ku byumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu bitangiye gukora ubushakashatsi, abantu bafite amagara mazima banduye HCoV-229E, bagize imbeho yoroheje.
Abarwayi bake bafite ubumuga bwo kutabara ni bo bagaragaza indwara ikomeye yo mu muhogo wo hasi.
SARS, nanone izwi nka "atypical pneumonia", ni yo yari icyorezo cya mbere cyanditswe neza mu mateka y'abantu cyatewe na HCoV, kandi icyateye iyo ndwara ni HCoV ya gatatu yavumbuwe, SARS-CoV.
Umuntu wa mbere wahuye na SARS mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyakwirakwiriye mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane, cyerekana ko abantu 774 bapfuye, abandi 8,096 bakaba barapfuye.
Uretse abafite ubwandu bwinshi, byemejwe ko hari n'ubundi bwandu bushobora kwiyongeraho hafi kabiri kuri buri kibazo, mu gihe cy'amajyambere y'urujya n'uruza rw'iminsi 4 kugeza kuri 7 n'ubwandu bwinshi bwa virusi bugaragara ku munsi wa 10 w'uburwayi.
Abarwayi banduye SARS-CoV bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'ibanze birimo ububabare mu myunzu, umutwe, umuriro, uburwayi n'imbeho, bikurikirwa n'ububabare bwo guhumeka, gucumba no guhumeka nabi.
Lymphopenia, imikorere y'umwijima itameze neza n'ubwiyongere bw'imikorere y'ibinyabutabire ni ibintu bisanzwe biba mu kigo cya SARS.
Ibyangiritse by'amaraso, gusakaza kwa epithelial cells no kongera imikorere y'imikorere na byo biragaragara mu barwayi ba SARS.
Abagera kuri 20-30% by'abarwayi nyuma yaho baba bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane no guhumeka.
Uretse imiyoboro yo mu rwego rwo hasi y'ubuhumekero, akenshi iyo habaye ibihuha by'udutsi twitwa cytokines, hari ibindi bice byinshi bishobora kwandura muri ibyo bihe bikomeye, harimo imiyoboro y'amaraso, impyiko n'impyiko, ibyo bikaba bishobora kuba byangiza cyane cyane abarwayi bafite ubwirinzi buke.
Virusi ya mbere yatandukanyijwe n'umuntu w'inshuti y'umurwayi w'ikimenyetso, binyuze mu gupima ibihaha by'umuntu wari waturutse i Guangzhou ajya i Hong Kong.
Kuva icyo gihe, ubushakashatsi ku cyorezo cya HCoV bwateye imbere cyane.
HCoV-NL63 yatandukanyijwe n'umwana w'amezi 7 mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2004 mu Buholandi.
Mu ntangiriro, byagaragaye ko ikwirakwira mu bana bato, abageze mu za bukuru n'abarwayi bafite ubumuga bwo guhumeka.
Indwara ziterwa na HCoV-NL63 zisanzwe zirimo inzara, guhuha, umuriro, na bronchiolitis.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ubudehe bundi, bwagaragaje ko virusi imwe yasamwe mu mazuru y'umwana w'amezi 8 wari urwaye pneumonia mu Buholandi.
Nubwo cyamenyekanye mu Buholandi, cyamaze gukwirakwira ku isi hose.
HCoV-NL63 itera indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero zigera kuri 4.7% kandi zigira ubukana mu ntangiriro z'impeshyi, mu itumba no mu itumba.
HCoV-NL63 ifitanye isano na interstitial acoustic-inflammatory, nanone yitwa croup.
Muri uwo mwaka, HCoV-HKU1 yatandukanyijwe n'umugabo w'imyaka 71 wari warakiriwe mu bitaro muri Hong Kong arwaye indwara ya Pneumonia na Bronchiolitis.
