Ubucuruzi bwo muri Ositaraliya bwagabanyije umubare w'impapuro z'isuku umuntu ashobora kugura icyarimwe
Ku mugoroba wo ku cyumweru no ku wa gatandatu, amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya yitwa Woolworths na Coles yagabanyije umubare w'impapuro z'isuku zishobora kugurwa icyarimwe mu maduka yabo yose ku rwego rw'igihugu, zigera kuri bibiri n'imwe.
Ku wa mbere, ALDI na yo yashyizeho imipaka y'ipakete rimwe.
Ibyo bihano byashyizwe ku mbuga za check-out no ku mbuga za Facebook z'iyi mikino.
Abaguzi bavuga ko bari gufatira hamwe ibicuruzwa mu gihe bari bakeneye kwigunga cyane kubera ubwoba bwa COVID-19.
Ku wa gatatu, Woolworths yagabanyije umubare w'abajya kugura impapuro z'isuku ku itegekonshinga rimwe, ndetse no ku byo gutanga mu rugo.
Mbere y'uko habaho ayo mavugurura, Woolworths na Coles byari byarabujije abantu kugura amakarito ane icyarimwe ku itariki ya 4 n'iya 5 Werurwe.
Mu itangazo ryasohowe ku wa 8 Werurwe, Coles yavuze ko nubwo itegeko ryo guhagarika amapaki ane ryakurikizwe, "ibigo byinshi bikomeje kubura ibicuruzwa mu gihe cy'isaha imwe yo kubitumiza", avuga ko ibyo bisabwa ari nta shingiro bifite, mu gihe ALDI yo yavuze ko ari "ibitunguranye" mu butumwa yoherereje kuri Facebook ku wa kabiri.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuvugizi wa Woolworths, mu cyumweru gishize, habonetse igiciro cy'ibicuruzwa cyazamutse cyane.
Ubucuruzi bwa Costco muri Canberra na bwo bwagabanyije umubare w'ibikoresho mu cyumweru gishize, bugera ku mapaketi abiri.
Mu rwego rwo kurushaho kugabanya ibura, Coles yasabye abacuruza ibicuruzwa byinshi kandi yongera inshuro zo gutumiza. Woolworths yasabye ibicuruzwa by'inyongera, naho ALDI ikomeza gukusanya ibicuruzwa kugira ngo itange ku wa Gatatu wihariye.
Umuyobozi wa Australian Retailers Association, Russell Zimmerman, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera imigabane, ariko ko bitoroshye kubera ko ubuyobozi bw'akarere bufite amategeko abuza abacuruzi gutumiza ibicuruzwa mu gihe cyagenwe.
