Yavuze ko impapuro z'isuku ari ikintu kiremereye, bityo ko nta bubiko bwinshi buhari, hanyuma, iyo ibicuruzwa byose byamaze kugurwa, amashuka manini asigaye asigaye ari ubusa, bituma abantu barushaho kumva ko hari ikibazo.
