Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe, kandi abantu banduye bashobora kuba bafite uburwayi.
Ibimenyetso bibiri by'ibanze ni umuriro (88%) n'igisebo cyumye (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara ni: umunaniro, guhumeka nabi, kumva nabi impumuro, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu bice by'umubiri no mu ngingo, kuribwa mu muhogo, umutwe, kugira imbeho, kuruka, guhumeka, gucibwamwo cyangwa gucibwamwo. Dukurikije WHO, hafi umuntu umwe muri batandatu arwara cyane kandi akagira ikibazo cyo guhumeka.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyandika ibimenyetso by'ubutabazi nk'ububabare bwo guhumeka, ububabare cyangwa igitutu gikomeje mu gatuza, guhungabana, kugora kubyuka, n'ubururu bw'amaso cyangwa iminwa; iyo ibimenyetso bibayeho, kwitabwaho byihutirwa.
Bamwe mu bantu banduye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi, ariko ibipimo byemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi batanze inama ko abantu bahuye n'abantu banduye bagombye gukurikiranwa hafi no gusuzumwa kugira ngo basuzume niba banduye.
Imibare y'Abashinwa igaragaza ko umubare w'abatazi Imana ari muto cyane, ariko ugera kuri 44 ku ijana.
Igihe cy'ubwiyongere busanzwe (igihe kiri hagati y'ubwandu n'intangiriro y'ibimenyetso) ni iminsi 1 kugeza ku 14; ni iminsi 5 gusa. Urugero rw'ubujiji, ni ugutekereza ku mugabane w'abantu bafite COVID-19 batakaje ubushobozi bwo kumva impumuro, mu ntangiriro wari 30% nyuma ugabanuka ugera kuri 15%.
Hari amakuru menshi agaragaza uko iyo ndwara yandura.
Iyi ndwara ivugwaho gukwirakwizwa ahanini n'udutonyanga duto duturuka ku guhanahana imibonano mpuzabitsina no mu gihe umuntu arimo ahekenya, asusumira cyangwa avuga; iyo umuntu ahana imibonano mpuzabitsina ari hagati ya metero 1 na 2 (metero 3 na metero 6).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko iyo umuntu anumye ntapfutse akanwa, ibyuya bishobora kuva kuri metero 4.5 (metero 15) kugeza kuri metero 8.2 (metero 27).
Hari abavuze ko virusi ishobora gukwirakwizwa n'udutonyanga duto duturuka mu kuvuga, tuguma mu kirere igihe kirekire. Udutonyanga tw'umwuka dushobora guturuka mu guhumeka, harimo no kuvuga, nubwo virusi idashobora gukwirakwizwa mu kirere.
Amashashi ashobora kugera mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'abantu bari hafi aho, cyangwa se ashobora kugera mu bihaha binyuze mu guhumeka.
Bimwe mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi, urugero nko kwinjiza mu mwuka no gukoresha umuti w'umutima (CPR), bishobora gutuma umuntu ahumeka vuba, bityo bikaba byatuma avura.
Ishobora gukwirakwira iyo umuntu akoze ku gice cyanduye, harimo n'uruhu, hanyuma agakora ku maso, ku zuru cyangwa ku munwa.
Nubwo hari impungenge ko ishobora gukwirakwira mu byondo, iki kibazo kiracyari gito.
Leta y'u Bushinwa yahakanye ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura mu byondo. Virusi yandura cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, nubwo ikwirakwira rishobora kuba mbere yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso no mu byiciro by'indwara nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso.
Abantu bapimwe neza barwaye indwara mu gihe cy'iminsi itatu mbere yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko hashobora kuba hari ubwandu mbere y'uko habaho ibimenyetso bikomeye.
