Uburyo bwo kugenzura icyorezo ni ukucyikumira cyangwa kugihashya, no kugihosha.
Gucunga indwara bikorwa mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo kandi bigamije kumenya abantu banduye, hamwe no gushyiraho izindi ngamba zo kugenzura ubwandu no gukingira kugira ngo indwara idahita ikwira mu baturage.
Iyo nta bushobozi bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara buhari, imihati ijya mu cyiciro cyo kugabanya: ingamba zifatwa kugira ngo ikwirakwira rigabanuke no kugabanya ingaruka zaryo ku rwego rw'ubuzima no ku muryango.
Uburyo bwo gukumira no kugabanya ubukana bw'iyo ndwara bushobora gukoreshwa mu buryo buhuje.
Gukumira bisaba ingamba z'ubutagondwa, kugira ngo icyorezo kigabanuke kigere ku mubare w'ubwangi mbere ya 1. Kimwe mu byo gukemura icyorezo cy'indwara zandura ni ukugerageza kugabanya ubukana bw'icyorezo, bizwi nka kugabanya icyorezo.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo guhungabanya serivisi z'ubuzima, kandi bigatuma haboneka igihe gihagije cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Ingamba z'ubutabazi zishobora gucunga icyorezo zirimo ingamba z'ubwirinzi ku muntu ku giti cye, nko kwirinda kwanduza intoki, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwicungira ukwacu; ingamba z'abaturage zigamije gukumira amacakubiri nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika gahunda z'amateraniro y'abantu benshi; uruhare rw'abaturage mu gushishikariza abantu kwemera no kwitabira ibyo ngamba; hamwe n'ingamba zo gukiza imyanda nk'iz'ibidukikije. Ingamba zikaze kurushaho zigamije kurwanya icyorezo zarakoreshejwe mu Bushinwa igihe ubukana bw'icyorezo bwagaragaraga, nko gushyiraho amategeko yo kugumana mu mijyi yose no gushyiraho ingamba zikomeye zo kugenda.
Ibindi bihugu na byo byafashe ingamba zitandukanye zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yatangije iperereza ku bwinshi no gushyira abantu mu kato, kandi itanga imiburo ku mibereho y'abanduye.
Singapore yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga ku bantu banduye biyemeje kwigumira mu kato, kandi ikagena ibihano bikomeye ku batayishyize mu kato.
Tayiwani yongereye umusaruro w'udupfukamunwa kandi ihana ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi. Ibigereranyo byakozwe n'u Bwongereza na Amerika bigaragaza ko hari imbogamizi zikomeye mu kugabanya (kugabanya icyorezo ariko ntihagire icyikumira) no kucyikumira (guhindura icyorezo).
Imigambi yo kugabanya indwara ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abantu bakenera ubuvuzi bw'ibanze ku bice bibiri bya gatatu, n'abapfa bakagabanukaho kimwe cya kabiri, ariko n'ubwo bimeze bityo, abantu babarirwa mu magana baracyapfa kandi uburyo bwo kuvura burakemangwa.
Gucika intege bishobora guhabwa umwanya w'ibanze, ariko bigomba gukomeza kugeza igihe virusi izakwira mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rumaze kuboneka, niba ari ubwa mbere), bitabaye ibyo, gucogora mu ngamba bizatuma ikwirakwira rihinduka vuba.
Gufata ingamba z'igihe kirekire zo guhashya icyorezo bitera ingaruka mu rwego rw'imibereho n'ubukungu.
Nta miti yihariye ya COVID-19 yemewe, ariko ubushakashatsi burimo gukorwa, harimo no kugerageza imiti isanzwe.
Gufata imiti ya gisilikare idakoreshwa n'abaganga, kunywa amazi no kuruhuka bishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'uburemere, umuti wa ogisijeni, intake z'amaraso n'ubufasha bwo guhumeka bishobora gukenerwa.
Gukoresha imiti ya Steroide bishobora gutuma ingaruka zayo zirushaho kuba mbi.
Imyinshi mu miti yemewe mbere yo kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi irimo gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS ivuga ko hari "uburyo busanzwe bwo kuvura mu rugo" bushobora gufasha mu guhangana n'ibimenyetso bya SARS-CoV-19.
Kongera ubushobozi no guhuza ubuvuzi ku bikenewe n'abarwayi ba COVID-19 byasobanuwe na WHO nk'ingamba z'ibanze zo guhangana n'icyorezo.
ECDC na ibiro by'akarere by'umuryango w'abibumbye byita ku buzima (WHO) by'i Burayi byasohoye amabwiriza ajyanye no kwimura umutungo mu bitaro no mu nzego z'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze ku byiciro bitandukanye, birimo: gushyira imbaraga mu gukora ibizamini bya COVID-19, guhagarika ibikorwa byo guhitamo igihe cyose bishoboka, gutandukanya no gutandukanya abarwayi banduye COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 binyuze mu guhugura abakozi no kongera umubare w'abafite imfashanyo n'ibitanda.
Hari ibitekerezo byinshi ku birebana n'aho ikibazo cya mbere (cyitwa "umurwayi wa zeru ") gishobora kuba cyarakomotse.
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanyeho icyorezo cya Coronavirus yamenyekanye tariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu mujyi wa Hubei mu gihugu cy'Ubushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wariyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Ibyo byabaga ahanini bifitanye isano n'isoko rya Hunan ry'ibyokurya by'inyanja, ryakundaga kugurisha inyamaswa zibayeho, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi yavuye mu nyamaswa z'ubwoko bumwe; cyangwa se, mu yandi magambo, ko ari iy'inkomoko y'inyamaswa. Igitsure cy'indwara y'ibicurane bitagaragara cyibonekeye ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza kandi cyitabwagaho n'umuganga Zhang Jixian mu bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei, cyamenyesheje CDC y'i Wuhan ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan baburiye bagenzi babo ku "virusi ya corona imeze nka SARS".
Abapolisi baburiye abaganga umunani, barimo Lee Wenliang, kandi undi muganga witwa I Feng, na we yahawe igihano n'abayobozi be, bamushinja ko yakwirakwije ibihuha.
Nyuma yaho, Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umugi wa Wuhan yatanze itangazo ku mugaragaro ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza, maze imenyesha OMS.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa mbere, mu gihe cy'icyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye kabiri hafi buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu zindi ntara z'Ubushinwa kubera urujya n'uruza rw'abantu n'umuvuduko w'imodoka mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'umuhanda munini w'imodoka.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwamenyesheje abantu bashya bagera ku 140 mu munsi umwe, barimo babiri mu mujyi wa Beijing n'umwe mu mujyi wa Shenzhen.
Imibare y'ubutegetsi nyuma yaho yerekana ko abantu 6,174 bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yarenze Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani ku mubare munini w'abamaze kwemezwa ko banduye ku isi. Ku itariki ya 9 Mata 2020, abasaga miliyoni 1.61 bari bamaze kumenyekana ku isi hose; abasaga 97,000 barapfuye, abasaga 364,000 barakira.
Ibihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200 bifite nibura umuntu umwe.
Kubera icyorezo mu Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza rw'abantu no gushyiraho imipaka.
Ibisubizo by'igihugu bikubiyemo ingamba zo kwirinda nk'ubwigenge (bimwe bizwi nka gahunda yo kuguma mu rugo, gahunda yo guhungira mu rugo, cyangwa gahunda yo gufunga). Kugeza ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300 muri Amerika cyangwa hafi 90% by'abaturage bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufunga, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo, n'abantu miliyari 1.3 mu Buhinde bari muri gahunda yo gufunga.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi hose bari mu bihe runaka byo gufunga, nyuma y'iminsi ibiri bigabanukaho miliyari 2.6 - ni ukuvuga hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko arwaye COVID-19 yabonetse i Wuhan ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019; raporo itaremezwa igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere wabonetse ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, umuganga Zhang Jixian yabonye abantu benshi barwaye indwara ya Pneumonia y'impamvu zitazwi, nyuma y'aho ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza, ibitaro bye byabwiye Wuhan Jiangnan CDC.
Ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza 2019, ibipimo bya mbere by'imiterere y'umubiri w'umurwayi byerekanye ko hari virusi ya corona imeze nka SARS.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza, Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umugi wa Wuhan yatanze itangazo rigenewe abantu bose.
Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (WHO) wabimenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
Nyuma y'ibi biganiro, abapolisi b'i Wuhan bari baraburiye abaganga "kutagira icyo bakwirakwiza" ku byerekeye iki cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta "gihamya idashidikanywaho" y'ikwirakwizwa ry'umuntu ku muntu.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije igikorwa cy'urugomo cyo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi, cyiswe "intambara y'abaturage" n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa Xi Jinping.
Mu byasobanuwe ko ari "igihombo gikomeye mu mateka y'abantu", ku wa 23 Mutarama, hatangajwe akarere ka Wuhan kafunze, kageza ku mijyi 15 muri Hubei, kagize ingaruka ku bantu miliyoni 57.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite byari bibujijwe mu mujyi.
Imikino yo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (itariki ya 25 Mutarama) yahagaritswe mu duce twinshi.
Abayobozi batangaje ko hari hagiye kubakwa ibitaro by'agateganyo, ari byo Hoshensen Hospital, byuzuye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hakorewe ikindi bitaro, ari cyo cyitwaga Leichensens Hospital, kugira ngo kijye cyakira abarwayi benshi.
Usibye ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 by'i Wuhan nk'ibigo by'amakoraniro n'ibibuga by'imikino, bikaba ibitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho ingamba z'inyongera zo gukumira icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga itangazo ry'ubuzima ku bantu batembera no kongera igihe cy'ikiruhuko cy'umunsi mukuru wa Spring.
Amashuri n'amashuri na byo byari byafunze mu gihugu hose.
Uturere twa Hong Kong na Macau twashyizeho ingamba nyinshi, cyane cyane ku birebana n'amashuri na za kaminuza.
Mu bice byinshi by'Ubushinwa, hashyizweho uburyo bwo gukora mu buryo bwa kure.
Imihango yo guhagarika ingendo mu mujyi wa Hubei no hanze yawo.
Imodoka rusange zari zaratunganyijwe, kandi amazu ndangamurage yo mu Bushinwa yose yari yarafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Mu mijyi myinshi, abantu bari bahagaritswe mu muhanda, kandi abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bageragejwe n'uburyo runaka bwo gufunga abantu hanze. Nyuma y'uko icyorezo cyageze ku rwego mpuzamahanga muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda ko virusi "iza" mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 yo kwigunga ku banyamahanga bose binjira mu mujyi. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, mu minsi itanu ishize, mu Bushinwa habaye umuntu umwe gusa wanduye mu gihugu, muri uru rugero akaba ari umuntu wari uturutse i Istanbul agarutse i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Premier w'u Bushinwa, Li Keqiang yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bwanduye mu gihugu cyabo ryahagaritswe kandi ko icyorezo cyahagaritswe mu Bushinwa.
Ku munsi w'ejo, nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho gahunda yo gufunga, ingendo mu bice bitandukanye by'u Bushinwa uretse Wuhan, zarorohewe. Minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku wa 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira ku bafite viza cyangwa ibyangombwa by'ubwenegihugu bizasubikwa guhera ku wa 28 Werurwe, ndetse nta makuru arambuye yerekeranye n'igihe iyi politiki izarangirira.
Abantu bashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri ambasade z'Ubushinwa.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yashishikarije ubucuruzi n'inganda kongera gufungura ku ya 30 Werurwe, itanga ibyangombwa by'inguzanyo ku bucuruzi. Inama y'igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo kwibuka, itangira saa kumi n'ebyiri z'umugoroba ku ya 4 Mata, n'umunsi w'icyunamo w'iminota itatu, mu gihe cya Qingming Festival, nubwo guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yasabye imiryango guhora yiteguye gutanga imihigo kuri interineti, bakurikiza amabwiriza yo gutandukanya abantu kugira ngo birinde icyorezo gishya cya COVID-19.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyemejwe ko cyandukiye Koreya y'Epfo kivuye mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habonetse ubwandu bwinshi, ahanini bitewe n'abantu benshi bari bateraniye mu mujyi wa Daigu, mu idini rishya ryitwa Yesu Shinchionji Church.
Shinchiji Bhakti wari uvuye i Wuhan ajya i Daigu, yari afite amakenga ku byerekeye inkomoko y'icyo cyorezo.
Kugeza ku ya 22 Gashyantare, 1,261 mu bayoboke 9,336 b'iri torero, cyangwa hafi 13%, bavuze ko bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ifite umuburo wo ku rwego rwo hejuru ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, muri Koreya habonetse abasaga 2000 byemejwe ko banduye, ku ya 29 Gashyantare habonetse abasaga 3150.
Inzego zose za gisirikare zo muri Koreya y'Epfo zahawe akato nyuma y'uko ibizamini byemeje ko abasirikare batatu banduye virusi.
Ibiganiro by'indege na byo byari byarafashwe, bityo bikaba byarahindutse. Porogaramu yashyizweho na Koreya y'Epfo, yabonwaga nk'irindi koranabuhanga rinini kandi ryiza ku isi mu gupima abaturage bakandura virusi, no gutandukanya abantu bose banduye, no gushakisha no gushyira mu kato abo bahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima bwari bukubiyemo kwemeza by'agateganyo ibimenyetso by'abantu bashya bageze mu mahanga binyuze kuri porogaramu za terefone, gupima byihuse virusi ku munsi ukurikiyeho hakoreshejwe ibisubizo, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 20,000 ku munsi.
Iyi gahunda ya Koreya y'Epfo, nubwo itarimo gushyiraho imijyi yose mu kato, ifatwa nk'intambwe mu kugenzura icyorezo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba Moon gufungwa, bavuga ko leta yarimo itunganya nabi icyorezo, cyangwa bashima uko yabyitwayemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo yari ifite ubwandu buke cyane bw'umunsi umwe mu byumweru bine.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byamenyeshejwe ko abimukira bose bashya bazatangwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri guhera ku ya 1 Mata.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku wa 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ibyifuzo by'ubufasha bw'igerageza rya virusi biturutse mu bihugu bitandukanye 121.
Irani yatangaje ku wa 19 Gashyantare, ko ifite ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwa mbere muri Kom, aho abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma y'aho, nk'uko bitangazwa na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi.
Mu ngamba za mbere zatangajwe na leta harimo gufunga ibitaramo by'umuziki n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, imikino, n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, ndetse no gufunga za kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri yisumbuye n'amashuri.
Irani yatanze miliyari 5 za Riyal zo kurwanya virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yatangaje ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twibasiwe n'icyorezo, ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi yatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo imodoka nyinshi zakomeje kugenda hagati y'imijyi mbere y'umwaka mushya w'Abaperesi, Navroz.
Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020, ingoro y'Abashiya i Qom yari ifunguye abagenzi. Muri Gashyantare, Irani yabaye ihuriro ry'icyorezo nyuma y'u Bushinwa.
Hagati y'ibyifuzo byo guhisha ingano y'icyorezo muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byabonye ko ibibazo byabo bifitanye isano na Irani kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, bigaragaza ko icyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha 388 by'abanduye byemejwe na leta ya Irani kugeza kuri uwo munsi.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yahagaritswe ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, ubwo 23 mu banyamuryango bayo 290 bapimwe ko banduye virusi.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura by'agateganyo abarwanashyaka b'uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe kubera imyigaragambyo y'amahoro, no kurekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zifite uburenganzira.
Yavuze ko inzego zifunze nk'ibigo by'ubwirinzi zifite ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwiza virusi, harimo no kutagira ubuvuzi buhagije.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, umubare munini wa mbere wigeze kuboneka mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki n'abategetsi ba leta 12 bo muri Irani, baba abahozeho cyangwa abahozeho, bari barapfuye bazize iyo ndwara.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, muri Irani habonekaga abarwayi bashya 50 buri saha, kandi buri minota 10 hapfaga umuntu umwe kubera coronavirus.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'umukozi wa WHO, Iran ishobora kuba ifite abarwayi benshi inshuro eshanu z'abari kubwirwa.
Hari kandi abavuga ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani bishobora kuba byaratumye igihugu kidakomeza kubona amafaranga yo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye w'Uburenganzira bwa Muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu byoroherezwa ibihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Icyorezo cyemejwe mu Butaliyani ku wa 31 Mutarama, ubwo ba mukerarugendo babiri b'Abashinwa bari i Roma bageragereshwaga SARS-CoV-2.
Abarwayi batangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose z'indege zivuye mu Bushinwa no gutangaza ko ari mu bihe by'ubukungu.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hatangiye kugaragara abarwayi 16 bemejwe mu karere ka Lombardy, hakagaragara itsinda ry'abarwayi ba COVID-19. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya ry'ubutabera ryo kurwanya iki cyorezo, rivanwaho abantu barenga 50,000 baturutse mu mirenge 11 itandukanye mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe, Giuseppe Conte, yagize ati "Mu turere dufite icyorezo, kwinjira no gusohoka ntibizatangwa.
Mu gihe hari hamaze gutangwa amabwiriza yo guhagarika ibikorwa by'akazi n'imikino muri utwo turere. Ku itariki ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'u Butaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza bifungwa burundu mu gihugu hose, kubera ko mu Butaliyani hapfuye abantu 100.
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'imikino ya Serie A, yagombaga kuba mu kwezi kwa kane nta bantu bayibonye, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yarahagaritswe burundu mu gihe cy'ukwezi.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse ko ibikorwa hafi ya byose by'ubucuruzi bihagarara, uretse amasuporari n'amafashini. Ku itariki ya 6 Werurwe, Ishuri ry'u Butaliyani ry'Ubuvuzi, Ubuvuzi, Gucika Indwara n'Ubuvuzi bw'Ikiremwamuntu (SIAARTI) ryasohoye amabwiriza arebana n'umuco w'ubuvuzi arebana n'amabwiriza agenga uburyo bwo gutandukanya abarwayi bakomeye bashobora gukoreshwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwasimbutse Ubushinwa mu gupima umubare munini w'abapfuye ba coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutangaza 3,405 bapfuye bazize icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko u Burusiya bwohereje indege icyenda z'ingabo zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari abantu 128,948 bemejwe, 15,887 bapfuye, naho 21,815 bakira, abenshi bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN yagaragaje ko guhuza umubare munini w'abageze mu za bukuru bo mu Butaliyani n'ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bari bafite virusi icyo gihe bishobora kuba byaratumye habaho urupfu rwinshi.
Igisubizo cy'Ubwongereza kuri virusi cyabanje kugaragara nk'icyoroshye mu bihugu byibasiwe, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'Ubwongereza ntiyari yarashyizeho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo gutandukanya abantu cyangwa gushyiraho ingamba zo gushyira abantu mu kato ku rwego rw'isi.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko leta yanenzwe kubera kubura umuvuduko n'ubushishozi mu gusubiza ibibazo abaturage bahura nabyo. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yasabye abantu guhagarika ingendo zose zidakenewe no guhuza imibereho, asaba abantu gukora bavuye mu rugo aho bishoboka, no kwirinda ahantu nko mu tubari, mu masoko y'imfatiro no mu mazu y'imyidagaduro.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, leta yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro nka pub na gym bigomba gufungwa vuba na bwangu, kandi isezeranya ko izishyura abakozi kugeza kuri 80% by'umushahara wabo, ku kigero cya £2,500 ku kwezi, mu rwego rwo gukumira ubushomeri mu bihe by'amakuba. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zo gushyiraho amabwiriza yo gukumira abantu cyane, aho yasabye abantu babiri cyangwa barenze kujya hamwe no kugabanya ibikorwa byo hanze ku bikorwa byemewe.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ingamba zabanje, izo ngamba zashyizweho n'abapolisi binyuriye mu gutanga ibihano no gutatanya imbaga y'abantu.
Ibigo byinshi by'ubucuruzi byategetswe gufunga uretse ibifatwa nk " ingenzi, birimo amasuporari, amaduka y'imiti, amabanki, amaduka acuruza ibikoresho by'ibikoresho, sitasiyo za peteroli n'amagare.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyemejwe bwa mbere mu ntara ya Pacific Northwest ya Washington, mu muntu wari waturutse i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Umutwe w'Ingabo zishinzwe kurwanya Coronavirus mu biro by'umukuru w'igihugu, The White House, washyizweho ku wa 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mu rwego rw'ubuzima rusange, kandi buhagarika ingendo z'abagenzi baturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura indwara - ikigo cy'ubutegetsi cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima rusange - cyatangaje ko cyateguye igikoresho cyacyo cy'igerageza.
N'ubwo Amerika yabigenje ityo, yatangiye igerageza buhoro, bituma bigorana gusobanukirwa uburebure nyakuri bw'icyorezo icyo gihe.
Ibigeragezo byabangamiwe n'ibikoresho by'ibipimo by'ibipimo byakozwe na leta ya FEBRUARI, kubura kwemerwa na leta ya FEBRUARI ku bikoresho by'ibipimo bitari ibya leta (bikorwa n'abanyeshuri, ibigo n'ibitaro), no gushyiraho amategeko agenga abantu kugira ngo babe bakwiriye kugeragezwa mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (nyuma yaho hagombaga gutangwa itegeko rya muganga).
Kugeza ku ya 27 Gashyantare, The Washington Post yatangaje ko muri Amerika hakorewe ibizamini bitarenga 4,000.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hatangijwe ibizamini bitarenga 14 000.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Associated Press cyatangaje ko "abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso kandi bafite icyemezo cy'umuganga, bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi kugira ngo bakore ikizamini". Nyuma y'aho leta ya Washington itangiriye gutanga raporo y'urupfu rwa mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko ari ho hashyizweho itegeko ry'ubutabazi, igikorwa cyagiye gikurikizwa n'izindi leta.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yasubitse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, kandi mu kwezi kwa gatatu, amashuri yo mu gihugu hose yari afunze. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, itsinda ry'inzobere mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo muri Imperial College London ryatanze inama kuri Amerika ku byerekeye ingengabihe y'icyorezo gishya cya coronavirus mu gihugu.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryo gutanga inkunga yo kwitegura no gusubiza icyorezo cya Coronavirus, riha agera kuri miliyari $8.3 mu nkunga y'ubutabazi ku bigo bya leta mu rwego rwo gusubiza iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yahagaritse ingendo z'abakozi, avanaho amakoraniro kandi atera abakozi inkunga yo gukorera mu rugo.
Imikino n'ibirori byarahagaritswe. Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko hari iminsi 30 yo guhagarika ingendo mu bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi, uretse mu Bwongereza.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yaguye ibihano abigeza mu Bwongereza no muri Ireland.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ubukungu cy'ubudehe, cyatumye amafaranga y'ishyaka ashobora gukoreshwa mu guhangana n'ikibazo.
Guhera ku ya 15 Werurwe, ubucuruzi bwinshi bwahagaritse imirimo cyangwa bugabanya amasaha y'akazi muri Amerika yose mu kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari cyemejwe mu bihugu byose 50 no mu ntara ya Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko i New York City hari abantu 10,700 banduye coronavirus, baruta umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko gutandukanya abantu byari bigiye gukora, kuko imibare y'abanduye yari imaze gukubitwa kabiri, ariko ikaba yariyongereye cyane, kuva ku minsi 2.0 kugeza ku minsi 4.7.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, i New York City hari abantu 32,308 bamaze kwemezwa ko banduye, naho 672 bahitanywe na virusi. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yari imaze gutanga amakuru y'ubwandu bwa coronavirus bwemejwe kurusha ikindi gihugu icyo ari cyo cyose ku isi, harimo u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani.
Nk'uko amakuru atangwa n'itangazamakuru abivuga, ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe, Perezida Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda kwitarura abandi kugeza ku itariki ya 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bwitwaga USNS Comfort, bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1.000, bwashyize ikirindiro i New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, muri Amerika habayeho impfu 884 z'abantu bishwe na coronavirus mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, umubare w'abanduye muri Leta ya New York warenze 100,000. White House yanenzwe kubera gupfobya ibyago no kugenzura ubutumwa binyuze mu gutegeka abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi guhuza imvugo n'ibitabo bya rubanda bijyanye na virusi n'ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Uburyo Trump akoresha mu gukemura ibibazo, buri mu buryo bumwe na bumwe burimo impande.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Amerika n'abatanga ibitekerezo banenze Amerika kubera ko ikomeza kwishingikiriza ku byangombwa by'ibanze by'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ibanze by'imiti, biva mu Bushinwa.
Igishushanyo mbonera cy'ingendo zo mu kirere cyakoreshejwe mu gusesengura no guhanura ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo, cyasohotse mu kwezi kwa mbere mu kwezi kwa mbere mu kinyamakuru The Journal of Travel Medicine.
Ishyirahamwe Mpuzamahanga ry'Inyambukiragutabara (IATA) ryagaragaje ko Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, na Taipei ari byo bihugu bya mbere byinjiye abagenzi benshi bivuye i Wuhan mu 2018.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne nabyo byatangajwe nk'ibibuga bikunzwe n'abantu baturuka i Wuhan.
Bali yagaragaye nk'urwa mbere mu mijyi 20 y'icyiciro cya mbere mu bijyanye no kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya yagaragaye nk'iya mbere. Australia yasohoye gahunda yayo yo guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) ku wa 7 Gashyantare.
Ibi byerekana ko nta byinshi byamenyekanye kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu kugenzura imipaka no gutumanaho mu gisubizo cy'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, mu gihugu cya Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko habayeho ikibazo cy'umutekano w'ibinyabuzima.
Kubera ubwikorezi bw'itumanaho rusange muri Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateguye gukura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba diplomasi mu karere, cyane cyane binyuze mu ngendo z'indege z'igihugu cy'iwabo, zatangajwe n'ubuyobozi bw'Ubushinwa.
Canada, Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Thailand ni byo bihugu bya mbere byari byateguye gucyura abaturage babyo.
Pakisitani yavuze ko itazongera kohereza abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yakuye Abanyakoreziya 34 cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo, usibye Abanyapolonye bane, Umunyamerika umwe n'Umuhinde umwe.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, u Bushinwa n'u Buhinde bavuye mu ndege muri Polonye, aho indege yo muri Brezili yahagaritse, hanyuma ikomeza urugendo yerekeza muri Brezili.
Abaturage ba Brazil bari bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasilia.
Kuri uwo munsi, abaturage 215 b'Abanyakanada (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere, na 39 bari mu yindi ndege yari yaraguzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan berekeza ku kigo cya CFB Trenton maze bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abanyakanada 185 ivuye i Wuhan, yageze ku cyambu cya CFB Trenton.
Abategetsi ba Australia bakuye abaturage 277 ku itariki ya 3 n'iya 4 z'ukwezi kwa Gashyantare, babajyana mu kigo cyo gufungirwamo ku kirwa cya Christmas, cyari cyarahinduwe ngo gibe ikigo cyo mu kato, aho bamaze iminsi 14.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, indege yo kwimura yavuye muri Nouvelle - Zélande igera muri Auckland; abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe baturutse muri Ositaraliya n'abo mu karere ka Pasifika) bari mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Whangaporoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Amerika yatangaje ko igiye gukuraho Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bw'ubwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abantu 129 b'Abanyakanada bari bavuye mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess, yageze i Trenton muri Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, guverinoma y'u Buhinde yatangiye guhungisha abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yari yaraguzwe na guverinoma ya Afurika y'Epfo, yasubijeyo abaturage 112 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo.
Ibizamini by'ubuvuzi byakozwe mbere yo kugenda, kandi Abanyafurika b'Epfo bane bagaragazaga ibimenyetso bya coronavirus basigaye inyuma kugirango bagabanye ibyago.
Abanyarwanda bavuye muri Afurika y'Epfo gusa bageragejwe.
Ibyavuye mu igerageza byatangaje ko Abanyafurika bose batanduye, harimo abagenzi, abapilote, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, bose bari kugenzurwa mu buryo bw'ubwitonzi kandi bari mu kato mu kigo cya The Ranch Resort mu gihe cy'iminsi 14.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukuraho igice cy'ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yavuze ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bifatanyije mu gufasha kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'Ubushinwa byibasiwe na virusi, bivugwa ko itsinda ry'abashyize hamwe mu karere ka Chicago ryohereje udupfukamunwa 50,000 tw'ibimenyetso by'uruhu (N95) mu bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje impano ya miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'Amerika ku kigo cy'ubuzima cya OMS, mu rwego rwo kurinda "abaturage bafite ibyago muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo", ndetse no gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku rukingo no mu mishinga yo kurukiza.
Interexon yatangaje ko guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 ku wa 6 Gashyantare, ubwo Senateri Richard Gordon yohererezaga Wuhan udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapore yatangaje ko izohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Abanyamerika mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni i Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje ko yatanze imyenda y'ubuvuzi miliyoni 18 mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi birimo amakanzu 10,000, Amerika yatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa kandi isezeranya inkunga y'amafaranga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'abahanga mu gufasha u Butaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho by'ipimisha bya miliyoni 1.1, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6, n'imyambaro 60,000 yo kurinda Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia, kugira ngo bitangirwe n'Umuryango wa Afurika yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yaho, yohereje muri Panama ibikoresho 5,000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibikoresho bitanu byo guhumeka.
Ma yanatanze imfashanyo y'imiti muri Canada. Ubuholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Czech bagaragaje impungenge ku masike n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yasubijeho ibikoresho 58 000 by'igerageza coronavirus byakozwe mu Bushinwa bifite igipimo cy'ubwiringiro cya 30% gusa, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwasubijeho udupfukamunwa 600,000 tw'Abashinwa twari dufite inenge.
U Bubiligi bwasubijeho udupfukamunwa 100.000 tw'ibikoresho by'umubiri byataye agaciro, byatekerezwaga ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, imfashanyo z'Abashinwa zakiriwe neza mu bice bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubutabazi by'ubutabazi by'ubutabazi mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye cyane imbaraga z'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa mu gucunga no gukumira icyorezo.
OMS yavuze itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu mwaka wa 2002-2004, aho abategetsi b'Abashinwa bashinjwaga ibanga ryatumye imihati yo kuyirinda no kuyikumira itangira, n'ikibazo cyo muri iki gihe aho leta y'u Burayi "yatangaga amakuru buri gihe kugira ngo yirinde gutinya mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'ukwezi".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ibanze cyo gushyiraho itegeko ryo gutwara abantu n'ibintu i Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gaudene Galia yavuze ko nubwo "nta gushidikanya ko WHO yari yarabitanze" byari "ikimenyetso gikomeye cyane cy'ubwitange bwo gukumira icyorezo aho cyibasiwe cyane" maze avuga ko ari "ikitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemezwa kw'ikwirakwizwa ry'abantu ku bantu no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'ibindi bibazo hanze y'Ubushinwa, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo mpuzamahanga cy'ubuvuzi rusange (PHEIC) gihangayikishije, kikaba ari icya gatandatu kuva icyorezo cya mbere cya Ebola cyafashwe mu mwaka wa 2009.
Tedros Adhanom, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa WHO, yavuze ko PHEIC yatewe n " "ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amafaranga make n'agati mu gihugu bidafite sisitemu z'ubuzima zikomeye.
Mu gusubiza ku ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'imihango yo kwirinda ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gushyiraho ingamba zitita ku ngendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "OMS idashishikariza guhagarika ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gufasha ibihugu bifite amikoro make mu kwitegura, ivuga ko ari ngombwa gufasha ibihugu "bifite uburyo bwo gutahura abantu banduye virusi, nubwo yaba igiye kugaragara".
Tedros yatangaje mu magambo ye y'inyongera ko "dukomeye gusa nk'aho turi mu rufatiro rw'abafite intege nke" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "kushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa se kuzishyura nyuma". Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, WHO mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru yashyizeho izina ry'indwara ya COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, Antonio Guterres, yemeye gutanga "ububasha bw'umuryango w'Abibumbye wose mu guhangana".
Ingaruka zabaye ugushyira mu bikorwa itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo, ryashyize hamwe igisubizo cy'umuryango w'abibumbye, nk'uko WHO ibivuga, bizatuma "bashobora kwibanda ku bisubizo by'ubuzima, mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora gukoresha ubuhanga bwazo mu guhangana n'ingaruka z'icyorezo ku rwego rw'imibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'ubutumwa bufatanyije riyobowe na OMS hamwe n'u Bushinwa ryashyizweho kugira ngo rifashe mu buyobozi bw'igihugu no gusura akarere kugira ngo ryeme "uburemere n'ubwandu bw'indwara" binyuze mu gukorana inama n'ibigo by'igihugu by'ingenzi no gusesengura "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza ku rwego rw'intara n'intara, harimo n'imijyi n'imidugudu". Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi igomba gukora cyane kugira ngo yitegure icyorezo cya coronavirus", ivuga ko nubwo ari kare cyane kuvuga ko ari icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba kuguma mu "cyiciro cyo kwitegura".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo kigenda kigaruka muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'ubumwe mu rwego rwo gusuzuma uko ibintu bimeze. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ku isi kizahabwa igipimo cyo kuva ku "cyinshi" kugeza ku "cyinshi cyane", kikaba ari cyo kigero cyo hejuru cyo kwitonda no gusuzuma ibyago.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi ushinzwe ibikorwa by'ubutabazi mu rwego rw'ubuzima muri WHO, mu itangazo yatanze yatanze, yatanze umuburo agira ati "iki ni ikigeragezo cy'ukuri kuri buri butegetsi ku isi: igihe kirageze ngo bukanguke.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi ugomba kwitegura", asaba ko ingamba zo gusubiza neza zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibibi kurusha ibindi".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko imibare iriho itakomeje kwemeza inzego z'ubuzima rusange gutangaza icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza bene ako kageni bizaba bisobanura "ko twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azagaragara kuri virusi".
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko WHO yari "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ubwiyongere bw'icyorezo n'uburemere bwacyo ndetse n'ubwiyongere bw'icyorezo". WHO yahuye n'ibitekerezo byinshi byo kuba icyorezo kitarakemutse, harimo gutinda gutangaza ko ari icyorezo cy'icyorezo no gutangaza ko ari icyorezo.
Mu byasabwe harimo inyandiko isaba ko Tedros Adhanom, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa WHO, yegura, yasinywe n'abantu 733.000 kugeza ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku wa 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu muri ONU zisaga icumi zemeje ko uburenganzira bwa buri muntu bugomba kubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo gukora ibikorwa by'ubutabazi kandi ko ibyo ari inshingano ya leta.
Itsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura umutungo cyangwa ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima bitagomba na rimwe gukoreshwa nk'impamvu yo kurobanura ku butoni ku bantu runaka.
Abahanga bashimangira ko buri wese, harimo abafite ubumuga, amoko mato, abageze mu za bukuru, abataye ingo, abatagira aho baba, abakennye, abafite ibibazo, impunzi n'andi matsinda atazwi akeneye ubufasha bwa leta, afite uburenganzira ku buzima.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ishinzwe kurwanya icyorezo cya COVID-19 irimo gukemura ibibazo by'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage.
Umuryango w'Ubukungu n'Ubukungu watangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru, ibitekerezo n'inama ku bisubizo by'amabwiriza mu gihe gikwiriye kandi mu buryo bunonosoye mu bihugu byo hirya no hino ku isi.
Kuva ku miyoborere kugeza ku gukomeza sisitemu z'ubuzima no ku bukungu bw'isi kugeza ku gukemura ingaruka z'ingendo n'ibihano, Digital Hub ikubiyemo Country Policy Tracker, kandi igamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga ku bindi no korohereza igisubizo cy'isi yose ku kibazo cya Coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenze uburyo Amerika, Minisitiri w'Abongereza ushinzwe ibiro bya Minisitiri w'Intebe, Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brazil, Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro, bakemuye icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei.
Abayobozi b'intara benshi b'ishyaka ry'aba-communist (CPC) ry'Ubushinwa birukanywe kubera ko bari barakoze ibikorwa byo gushyira abantu mu kato mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, mu rwego rwo kugaragaza ko batishimiye uko inzego za politiki zabyitwayemo mu gihe habaga harabaye iki cyorezo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko icyo cyemezo cyari kigamije kurinda Xi Jinping, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, uburakari bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Abashinwa, nka Zhao Lijian, banze kwemera ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan, bashyigikira imigambi y'uko COVID-19 ishobora kuba yaraturutse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubuyobozi bwa Donald Trump muri Amerika buvuga ko coronavirus ari "umugera w'Abashinwa" cyangwa "umugera wa Wuhan", buvuga ko "ubutegetsi bw'u Bushinwa bwahindura virusi icyorezo ku isi", bamwe mu banenga bavuga ko ari ivangura ry'amoko n' "ibinyoma by'ubutegetsi bwe mu kurwanya indwara".
Ikinyamakuru The Daily Beast cyakiriye telegaramu ya leta ya Amerika igaragaza ko hari ikibazo cy'itumanaho cyakomotse ku nama y'umutekano y'igihugu, ivuga ko "byose byibanda ku Bushinwa.
Turasabwa kugerageza gutanga ubutumwa mu buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose, harimo ikiganiro n'amateraniro y'abanyamakuru na televiziyo. "Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Politiki Mpuzamahanga na Bloomberg byatangaje ko ingamba z'Ubushinwa zo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byibasiwe na virusi ari kimwe mu bigize propagande yo kongera imbaraga ku isi.
Umuyobozi w'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga, Joseph Borel, yaburiye ko hari "ikintu cya politiki gihereranye n'imibereho y'abantu, harimo guharanira kugira ingaruka binyuriye ku mpinduka no 'gutegeka mu buryo burangwa n'ubwitange.'
Borrell yongeyeho ko "Ubushinwa bwiyemeje gushyira imbere ubutumwa bw'uko, mu buryo butandukanye na Amerika, ari cyo gihugu gifite inshingano kandi cyiringirwa".
Ubushinwa bwasabye kandi Amerika gukuraho ibihano kuri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, ibi bihugu bibiri bya nyuma bikaba byarahawe inkunga.
Impano ya Jack Ma y'ibirashe 100,000 by'ubumara yageneye Cuba yahagaritswe n'ibihano by'Amerika ku itariki ya 3 Mata.
Abategetsi b'Amerika na bo bashinjwa ko bahindura imfashanyo zigenewe ibindi bihugu zikaba ari zo zigenewe igihugu cyabo.
Kandi hari ibindi bihugu byagiye bigirana amakimbirane ku bijyanye n'udupfukamunwa, urugero nka: Ubudage, Otirishiya na Suisse; Repubulika ya Tchèque n'Ubutaliyani.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe za ventilateurs amagana zari zigenewe muri Espagne.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yanenze ko EU idafite ubumwe n'u Butaliyani bwazahajwe na coronavirus.
Maurice Massari, Ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani muri EU, yavuze ko "Ubushinwa bwonyine ari bwo bwatanze igisubizo ku buryo bwa bilateral.
Birumvikana ko ibyo bidatanga ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubwiyunge bw'u Burayi".
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma y'ikiganiro cya telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani, Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'Uburusiya Vladimir Putin yateganyije kohereza abasirikare b'ingabo z'Uburusiya, imodoka zihariye zo kugabanya ubwandu n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo amagambo y' "umuntu ukomeye mu bya politiki " atavuzwe izina, kivuga ko 80 ku ijana by'imfashanyo zatanzwe n'u Burusiya "byari ubusa cyangwa ko nta cyo byari byatanze ku Butaliyani. "
Uwo muyobozi yashinje u Burusiya ko bukora ibikorwa by " "ubushakashatsi mu by'ubukungu n'ubutegetsi".
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'u Butaliyani, Luigi Di Meo, bahakanye ibivugwa n'itangazamakuru, ndetse banashimira.
Uburusiya bwohereje imfashanyo z'ubuvuzi muri Amerika mu ndege y'ibyangombwa.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko "mu gihe [Putin] arimo atanga ubufasha ku bafatanyabikorwa be b'Abanyamerika, atekereza ko igihe abacuruzi b'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho by'ibanze bo muri Amerika bazongera umusaruro, bazaba bashobora no kwishyura mu gihe bibaye ngombwa".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO "Defender 2020", ni yo myitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO ikomeye cyane kuva intambara y'ubukonje irangiye, izabera mu Budage, Polonye, n'ibihugu bya Baltique, ku rwego rwo hasi.
Kate Hudson, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango wita ku Bihereranye n'Ibirwanisho bya Nikleyeri, yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020 agira ati "muri iki gihe cy'ibibazo by'ubuzima rusange, ntabwo iteza akaga ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi gusa, ahubwo iteza akaga n'abaturage bo mu bihugu biwugize aho bakorera".
Perezida wa Irani, Hassan Rouhani, yanditse ibaruwa igenewe abantu bose ku mugaragaro ku bayobozi b'isi ku wa 14 Werurwe 2020 asaba ubufasha, avuga ko igihugu cye kirimo kugorwa no kurwanya icyorezo kubera ko kitagishoboye kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga bitewe n'ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani. Iki cyorezo cyateye Amerika gusaba ko yakurikiza politiki z'imibereho myiza kimwe n'ibindi bihugu bikize, harimo kwita ku buzima busanzwe, kwita ku bana bose, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango gihemba, n'amafaranga menshi yo kwita ku buzima rusange.
Abahanga mu bya politiki bavuze ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku isubirwamo rya Donald Trump mu matora ya perezida yo mu 2020. Imishyikirano ya diplomasi hagati y'u Buyapani na Koreya y'Epfo yarushijeho kuzamba kubera icyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "imihati yo gushyira abantu mu kato idasobanutse kandi idakorwa" y'u Buyapani ubwo yatangazaga ko umuntu wese uvuye muri Koreya y'Epfo azashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri mu duce twashyizweho na leta.
Mu mizo ya mbere, abaturage bo muri Koreya y'Epfo bari bagabanye ibitekerezo ku birebana n'ukuntu Perezida Moon Jae - in yari yitabiriye icyo kibazo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba Moon kwiregura, bavuga ko leta yarimo itunganya nabi icyorezo, cyangwa bashima uko yabyitwayemo. Iki cyorezo cyatumye ibihugu bishyiraho amategeko y'ubutabazi mu buryo bwo kwitabira.
Hari bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bagize impungenge ko bishobora gufasha leta gukomeza ubutegetsi.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yayo yemeye ko Minisitiri w'Intebe, Viktor Orbán, ategeka igihe kitarondoreka, ihagarika inteko ishinga amategeko ndetse n'amatora, kandi igahana abantu bagaragaye ko bakwirakwiza amakuru y'ibinyoma ku byerekeye virusi n'uburyo bwo guhangana n'ikibazo ndetse na guverinoma.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyagaragaye ko aricyo cyateje ibibazo byinshi by'ibura ry'ibikoresho byo kurwanya icyorezo ku isi, kugura biturutse ku bwoba, no guhungabanya ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikorwaremezo.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze umuburo ku kibazo cy'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'uko abaguzi bakomeje kubyifuza ndetse n'abacuruza bakibura ibicuruzwa.
Mu turere twinshi, habaye n'ubucuruzi buturutse ku bwoba, bituma ibintu by'ibanze by'ibanze nk'ibyokurya, impapuro z'isuku n'amazi yafashe mu mazi yafashe mu mazi, biva ku ntebe z'ububiko, bituma ibyokurya bigabanuka.
Uruganda rw'ikoranabuhanga rwihariye rwaburiwe ko gutwara ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki byatinda.
Nk'uko byatangajwe na Tedros Adhanom, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa WHO, ngo ibyifuzo by'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyabo byiyongereye inshuro 100.
