Ibizamini bya laboratwari by'indwara ya coronavirus yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi ihura na SARS-CoV-2 birimo uburyo bwo kumenya niba virusi iriho, n'uburyo bwo kumenya niba hari udukoko tw'ubwirinzi twakozwe mu gihe cy'ubwandu.
Kujya mu bipimo by'ubwandu byemezwa na RT-PCR, igaragaza RNA ya coronavirus.
Iki cyangombwa ni icy'umwihariko kandi kigamije gusa kumenya RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu buherutse cyangwa bukiri muzima.
Gushakisha ingufu z'umubiri (Hematopoiesis) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima indwara no kugenzura abantu.
Ibizamini by'ubwirinzi byerekana umubare w'abantu basanganywe indwara, harimo n'abari bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyane ku buryo bitagaragara cyangwa se batagiraga ibimenyetso.
Ibipimo by'iyi myigaragambyo bishobora gutuma hagaragara umubare nyawo w'abapfa n'uko abantu bakwirakwiza ubwirinzi.
Kubera ko ibipimo by'abantu batageze ku kigero cyo hejuru, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi mu bantu kugeza muri Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyigeze gikora ibizamini birenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari ubusumbane bwinshi ku gipimo cy'ibizamini mu bihugu bitandukanye.
Iri tandukaniro rishobora kandi kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku gipimo cy'imfu z'abatangajwe, bikaba bishoboka ko mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe byitezweho byinshi.
Hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo guhindura imiterere y'ibinyabiziga mu gihe nyacyo (rRT-PCR), ibipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe hakoreshejwe uburyo butandukanye, harimo n'ibyavuye mu musarani cyangwa mu byondo, bishobora gusuzumwa.
Ubusanzwe, ibisubizo biboneka mu masaha make cyangwa mu minsi ibiri.
RT - PCR ikorwa mu gihe cy'icyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara ni yo igaragaza ko umuntu afite ubushobozi bwo kwivuza.
Nyuma y'aho, virusi ishobora kuva mu muhogo, mu gihe ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu banduye bagenzurwa mu cyumweru cya kabiri, mu buryo bw'amahitamo, ibikoresho by'igishushanyo bishobora gukoreshwa mu guhumeka cyangwa mu guhumeka (umunyururu).
Kimwe mu bipimo bya mbere bya PCR bikoresha imikorere y'igihe nyacyo yo guhindura inyuguti ya polymerization (rRT-PCR) cyatangijwe muri Mutarama 2020 i Berlin muri Charité, kikaba cyashingiweho gutanga ibikoresho 250,000 byatanzwe n'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
Ubwongereza nabwo bwari bwakoze ibizamini by'ubushakashatsi ku wa 23 Mutarama 2020. Ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo cya Koganbiotech cyakoze ibizamini by'ubushakashatsi ku wa 28 Mutarama 2020, mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi, bishingiye kuri PCR SARS-CoV-2 (Powercheck Coronavirus).
