Gukaraba intoki buri gihe mu gihe cy'umunsi "mu gihe cy'ibyihutirwa" bigabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'ubushye no gucibwamwo, zikwirakwizwa mu nzira y'umwanda.
Abantu bashobora kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'ibicurane cyangwa imbeho, mu gihe batigeze bakaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, ku zuru cyangwa ku munwa (ni ukuvuga mu maso).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa: mbere na nyuma yo kujya koga, nyuma yo gukaraba umwana cyangwa guhindura isura, mbere yo kumuhereza ibyokurya, mbere yo kurya, mbere na nyuma yo gutegura amafunguro cyangwa kurya inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Niba nta mazi n'isabune biboneka, intoki zishobora gukoreshwa mu gusukura intoki. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasabye ko abantu bakaraba intoki mu bihe bikurikira:
Mbere yo gutegura amafunguro, mu gihe cyo kuyateka na nyuma yo kuyateka.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Nyuma yo guhindura impapuro z'ibanga cyangwa gusukura umwana ukoresha ubwiherero.
Nyuma yo gusokoza, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ibiribwa cyangwa imyanda.
Isuku y'amaboko y'abaganga yerekeza ku myitozo y'isuku ifitanye isano n'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa ubuvuzi bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego y'ibanze yo gukaraba intoki ni ukuvana mu ntoki indwara ziterwa n'udukoko (bakteriya, virusi, cyangwa izindi mikorobe zishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho bishobora gutera uburwayi cyangwa se ubwonko.
Ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakoresha ibiribwa cyangwa mu by'ubuvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo: kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'ibicurane, virusi ya corona n'izindi; gukumira indwara z'ibicurane ziterwa n'ububyimba; kugabanya indwara z'ubuhumekero;
no kugabanya umubare w'abana bapfa mu gihe cyo kubyarira mu rugo.
