Indi mimerere aho gukaraba intoki mu buryo bukwiriye byagombye gukoreshwa mu kwirinda kwanduza indwara, ni: mbere na nyuma yo kuvura igisebe cyangwa igisebe; nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa gusokoza; nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'amatungo cyangwa gukorakora amatungo; na nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, umubare w'abantu bakaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune ni muto.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2015 ku bihereranye no gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 bwagaragaje ko ku kigereranyo, imiryango 38.7% yakoreshaga isabune mu gukaraba intoki. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabia Saudite ari yo yari ifite igipimo cyo hejuru cy'abantu 97 ku ijana; muri Amerika ni ho hari igipimo cy'abantu 77 ku ijana; mu Bushinwa ho ni ho hari igipimo cyo hasi cyane cy'abantu 23 ku ijana.
Gahunda y'ubuzima bw'ibanze yashyizweho mu bikorwa n'ishami ry'uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa by'ingamba zikomeye mu guteza imbere ubuzima n'uburezi bw'abana.
Iyi gahunda y'igihugu y'ibanze ikubiyemo gukaraba amenyo buri munsi hakoreshejwe fluoride, gukaraba intoki buri munsi hakoreshejwe isabune, no gufata imiti yo kurwanya udukoko kabiri mu mwaka.
Nanone kandi, byashyizwe mu bikorwa muri Indoneziya.
Gukoresha amazi arimo isabune cyangwa umuti w'isuku bishobora gutuma udukoko duto duto tuva mu ruhu.
Igikorwa cy'ibanze cya sabuni n'umutobe ni ukugabanya imbogamizi mu muti, no kongera ubura.
Amazi yonyine ni umuti udakoresha neza mu gusukura uruhu, kubera ko ibinure na poroteyine, ari byo bigize ubutaka bw'ibinyabuzima, bidashobora gushonga mu mazi mu buryo bworoshye.
Icyakora, gutunganya amazi bifashishwa no kuyatanga mu buryo buhagije.
Kubera ko isabune ikomeye ikoreshwa kenshi, ishobora kuba irimo udukoko twasigaye mu mikoreshereze ya mbere.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko nta mikorobe ishobora guhitana mikorobe mu gihe yaba yavuye mu mazi.
Nyamara kandi, CDC ivuga ko "isabune irimo umuti ushobora guterera amazi mu biganza by'umuntu nta bikoresho by'amaboko bifite icyo bivuze".
Hari gahunda yo gukangurira abantu kumenya ko bafite intabwe.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya igaragaza ko gukoresha imiti ya Antibacterial cyangwa se umuti wa Antibacterial bishobora gutuma habaho imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byirinda imiti.
Icyakora, isabune z'ubumara zirimo imiti isanzwe yo kurwanya mikorobe, urugero nka triclosan, irimo ubwoko bwinshi bw'ibinyabuzima byirinda mikorobe.
Bityo rero, nubwo amasabune arwanya mikorobe adashobora gutuma habaho ubwoko bw'imiti idashobora kurwara indwara, ntashobora kugira ingaruka nk'uko bigaragazwa.
Uretse imyuka ituma umuntu ahumeka n'ibirinda uruhu, uburyo bwateye imbere bushobora kuba burimo amoko (amoko ya acetic, ascorbic, lactic), amoko ya benzoic afite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya mikorobe n'ibindi bifasha uruhu guhinduka (aloe vera, vitamine, menthol, umusaruro w'ibimera). Ubushakashatsi bwimbitse bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Oregon School of Public Health bwagaragaje ko isabune isanzwe ifite mikorobe z'ibanze ari nziza nko mu kwirinda indwara no kwirukana mikorobe mu biganza, kimwe n'isabune zisanzwe z'ibikoresho by'abaguzi.
Amazi ashyushye kandi meza yo gukaraba intoki ntaba ashyushye bihagije kugira ngo yice mikorobe.
Iyo umubiri ufite ubushyuhe bwa dogere 37 z'isumbuye, mikorobe zikura cyane.
Icyakora, amazi ashyushye afite isabune ni ingirakamaro cyane kurusha amazi akonje afite isabune mu gukuraho ibinyabutabire n'ibinyabutabire biyirimo.
Icyakora, binyuranye n'uko abantu benshi babyemera, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe bwagaragaje ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye nta ngaruka bigira ku kugabanya mikorobe ku biganza.
Umunyunyuzi w'intoki cyangwa umuti wo kugabanya ubukana bw'intoki ni umuti wo gusukura intoki ufite urufatiro rutagira amazi.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya za 90 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki bitagira amazi (byitwa kandi intoki z'amavuta, intoki z'amavuta cyangwa intoki z'ibikoresho by'isuku) byatangiye gukundwa.
Inyinshi muri izo isopropylate ziba zishingiye kuri alkali cyangwa ethanol, zikoreshwa mu buryo bworoshye no kugabanya ingaruka zo gukama kwa alkali, zikoreshwa mu buryo bwa gels, urugero nka karbomer (polymerize ya acrylic acid), cyangwa mu buryo bw'umwikubo cyangwa mu busa, urugero nka moisturizer, hamwe na glycerine.
Guhuriza hamwe umwimerere wa hidrogeni-peroxide bituma ibikorwa byo kurwanya mikorobe birushaho kwiyongera.
Inzoga z'ibinure zisukura udukoko, udukoko twangiza umubiri (MRSA na VRE), uburwayi bw'ibicurane n'izindi virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo virusi ya HIV, herpes, RSV, virusi z'impfizi z'ingore, vaccinia, influenza na hepatite) n'izindi ndwara z'ibyorezo.
Inzoga z'ibirahuri zirimo 70% by'inzoga zirimbura 99,97% by'udukoko nyuma y'amasegonda 30 zishyiriweho (ni nka 3.5 log minus, ni nka 35 decibel minus) na 99,99% na 99,999% by'udukoko nyuma y'iminota 1 zishyiriweho (ni nka 4 na 5 log minus). Inzoga z'intoki ni zo zikora cyane ku dukoko ndetse ni nke ku mikorobe zimwe na zimwe.
Inzoga zikorana n'intoki zidakora neza ku bwoko bwa norovirus (cyangwa Norvoc) bw'ubwandu bw'intoki, ari na zo mpamvu zisanzwe zitera indwara z'ubuhumekero. Inzoga zikoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki cyangwa mu gukaraba intoki zikwiye gukoreshwa mu buryo bworoshye kugira ngo intoki zombi zibe zikinze cyangwa zigizwe n'inkweto.
Imbere n'inyuma y'amaboko yombi, hagati n'intoki zose, bisukurwa mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30, kugeza igihe amazi, imyanda cyangwa ingeri bikamye.
Inshyi z'intoki na zo zigomba gukaraba neza mu biganza byombi. Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki aho gukaraba intoki, cyane cyane iyo intoki zigaragara ko zanduye.
Gukoresha izi reagents mu buryo bwagutse bishingiye ku buryo bworoshye zikoreshwa no ku buryo zihita zangiza mikorobe; ariko, ntizikwiye gukoreshwa nk'uburyo bwo gusukura intoki mu buryo bukwiriye keretse gusa iyo habonetse isabune n'amazi.
Gukoresha kenshi ibiyobyabwenge by'amaboko bikoresha inzoga bishobora gutuma uruhu rugira isuku keretse hagize ibiyubaka cyangwa se ibimukomeza uruhu byongerwa muri formule.
Ingaruka zo kumesa inzoga zishobora kugabanuka cyangwa kuzimanganywa no kongeramo glycerin na/cyangwa ibindi bintu byongerera amavuta mu mwandiko.
Mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi, isuku y'uruhu n'umwimerere byaragabanutse cyane ugereranyije n'isabune cyangwa imiti yo guhanagura udukoko.
Kimwe mu bintu bidakunze gutera indwara z'uburwayi, ni indwara y'uburwayi bw'uruhu, urticaria cyangwa se indwara yo kwiheba.
Kuba abantu bakunze guhura n'abantu bafite indwara z'uruhu zitera ububabare kurusha gukaraba intoki n'isabune n'amazi, byaje kuba ikintu gishishikaje.
N'ubwo ari ingirakamaro, ibikoresho bitagira amazi ntibisukura ibintu bihumanya ku ntoki, ahubwo bibikuraho indwara gusa.
Ni yo mpamvu ibikoresho byo gusukura intoki bitagira ingaruka mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara zandura nk'isabune n'amazi, kubera ko izo ndwara zikomeza kuba ku ntoki.
Ingaruka z'ibisukika by'amaboko bitagira inzoga zishingira cyane ku bikoresho n'uburyo bikoreshwa, kandi mu mateka zagiye zidakora neza cyane kurusha inzoga n'ibinyobwa bisukika.
Mu bihe bya vuba aha, mu buryo bunyuranye n'inzoga, igaragazwa ko ifasha mu kugabanya ingaruka nyuma yo gukoreshwa kenshi, kubera ko ishobora gutera ibibazo by'uruhu byateye imbere, uburyo bukoresha benzalkoniyumu chloride bwagaragajwe ko bufite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya mikorobe buhoraho kandi bwigaragaza nyuma yo gukoreshwa.
Abantu benshi bo mu midugudu ifite amikoro make ntibashobora kugura amasabune, ahubwo bakoresha ivu cyangwa ibumba.
Umukungugu cyangwa ibumba bishobora kugira ingaruka nziza kurusha amazi yonyine, ariko bikaba byangiza cyane kurusha isabune.
Hari impungenge ko iyo ubutaka cyangwa ivu byandujwe na mikorobe bishobora gutuma indwara ikwirakwira aho kugabanya.
Kimwe n'isabune, umwotsi ni umuti wica udukoko kuko iyo uhuye n'amazi, uba urimo umuti urimo umunyu.
OMS yashyizeho umwotsi cyangwa umucanga nk'uburyo bwo guhinduranya isabune mu gihe nta sabuni iboneka.
Uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki, nk'uko bitangazwa n'Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no kurwanya indwara, ni ukubanza gukaraba intoki:
Jya wotsa intoki amazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Amazi atemba ni yo y'ingenzi kubera ko imigezi ifite amazi adakama ishobora kwanduzwa, nubwo ubushyuhe bw'amazi nta cyo bwaba buvuze.
Gushyiraho urugero rukwiye rw'isabune, usige ku ntoki, ushyireho n'ibiganza, hagati y'intoki n'amaboko, n'amaboko.
Isabuni ikuraho udukoko twanduye mu ruhu, kandi ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko abantu bakaraba intoki neza cyane iyo bakoresheje isabune aho gukoresha amazi yonyine.
Fata iminota 20 nibura.
Gushwanyaguza bituma habaho gusambana, bigatuma udukoko duto duto tuva mu ruhu, kandi iyo umuntu amaze igihe kirekire asambana, bituma haboneka udukoko twinshi.
Jya ukaraba neza munsi y'amazi atemba.
Gukaraba mu kibaya bishobora kongera kwanduza intoki.
Goma ukoresheje igitambaro gisukuye cyangwa se ureke bikome mu kirere.
Ibiganza byumutse kandi byanduye birushaho kwanduzwa. Ibibanza by'ibanze bikunze kurenga ni ibiganza by'iburyo, intoki, hagati y'intoki n'amaboko y'intoki.
Amagi y'ibishushanyo n'ibishushanyo by'amaboko bishobora gucumbikira udukoko duto.
Akenshi, umuti wo gusiga intoki mu mazi ukoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki, ni wo utuma intoki zidakomera; kugira intoki zikomeye bishobora gutuma uruhu rugira ibikomere bishobora kongera ibyago byo kwandura.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere aho amazi y'amazi n'isabune ataboneka, mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, hashobora kuboneka uburyo butandukanye bw'amafaranga make bwo koroshya gukaraba intoki, urugero nko gushyira amazi mu nkono cyangwa mu mazi mu gikoni gifite imyobo ikwiriye, no gukoresha ivu. Mu mimerere y'amazi aciriritse (nk'amashuri cyangwa uturere two mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari uburyo bwo kubungabunga amazi, urugero nk'"utuzi tw'amazi" n'ubundi buryo bw'amafaranga make.
Tippi - tap ni uburyo bworoshye bukoresha igiti gihanitse ku mugozi, n'ubufasha bw'ikirenge kugira ngo gitange amazi make ku ntoki no ku nkingi y'isabune.
Kumesa intoki neza ni kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi bigize isuku y'intoki, ariko hari impaka zimwe na zimwe ku buryo bwo kumesa intoki mu byumba bya rubanda.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwagaragaje ko utuyoboro tw'impapuro dutuma umuntu agira isuku nyinshi kurusha utwo dukoresho tw'amashanyarazi dusukura intoki, dusanga mu byumba byinshi by'ubwiherero.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Westminster, mu mujyi wa Londres, bwatewe inkunga n'uruganda rw'ibikoresho by'impapuro, European Tissue Symposium, bwari bugamije kugereranya urwego rw'isuku rutangwa n'ibikoresho by'impapuro, imashini zimesa intoki zishyushye n'imashini zimesa intoki z'ubwoko bwa jet-air.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki no kuzisukura hakoreshejwe akuma gashyushye, umubare w'ibinyabutabire wariyongereyeho 194% ku ntoki no 254% ku biganza.
Gutakaza imyenda hakoreshejwe imashini zikorera mu kirere byongereye umubare w'udukoko ku kigero cya 42% ku ntoki no kuri 15% ku biganza.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki no kuzisukura n'utuwugi tw'impapuro, umubare wose w'udukoko wagabanutseho 76% ku ntoki no ku biganza ku kigero cya 77%. Abahanga mu bya siyansi bakoze n'ibizamini kugira ngo bamenye niba uburyo bwo gusukura buri bwoko bw'intoki bwagize ingaruka ku bandi bakoresha ubwiherero n'ibidukikije by'ubwiherero.
Ikigo gitukura indege, gitanga umwuka uturutse muri iyo kompanyi ku muvuduko ugereranywa na 180 m/s (650 km/h; 400 mph), cyashoboraga guhumeka mikorobe mu ntoki no muri iyo kompanyi, kandi gishobora kwanduza n'abandi bakoresha ubwiherero ndetse n'aho bakorera mu bwiherero, ku metero 2 uvuye aho bari.
Gukoresha imashini zimesa intoki zishyushye byatumaga mikorobe zikwirakwira kugeza kuri metero 0.25 z'iyo mashini.
Imyenda y'impapuro ntiyagaragaje ikwirakwira ry'ibinyabuzima by'ibanze. Mu mwaka wa 2005, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt und Umwelt, bwagaragaje uburyo butandukanye bwo kumesa intoki.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, imibare y'ibinyabuzima byanduye yahindutse ikurikira:
Hariho abahanga batandukanye mu gukora imashini zimesa intoki, kandi imashini zimesa intoki zagereranyijwe no gukaraba impapuro.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umuti wo gukaraba intoki mu gihe cy'urugendo, mu gihe nta mazi n'isabune bihari.
Inzoga z'amaboko zikorana na alcohol zigomba kuba zifite nibura 60% by'inzoga.
Guhana intoki mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi byabaye ngombwa nyuma y'igihe kirekire Ignaz Semmelweis, umuganga w'Umuhungari, avumbuye ko ari ingirakamaro mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro (mu wa 1846).
Hari ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bitanga ibitekerezo byibutsa abakozi b'ibitaro ko bagomba gukaraba intoki mu gihe bibaye ngombwa.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko gukoresha izo nkingo byagabanyije umubare w'abandura.
Mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi, intoki zirogezwa mu gihe cy'amasegonda 15, zikagira imyanda ikoreshwa n'isabune n'amazi cyangwa se gel mu rugero rukwiriye, kandi buri gice cy'intoki kigasukwa.
Inzoka z'amaboko yombi zigomba gukorana.
Niba hari ibisigazwa munsi y'imisumari, burashi y'umusatsi ikomeye ishobora gukoreshwa mu kuyikuramo.
Kubera ko mikorobe zishobora kuba mu mazi ku biganza, ni ngombwa ko bikaraba neza kandi bikayomeka n'ikibanza gitunganye.
Nyuma yo gukama, igikoresho cy'impapuro kigomba gukoreshwa mu gufunga amazi (kandi niba ari ngombwa, irembo ryose ry'umwobo rigomba gufungurwa).
Ibyo bituma intoki zitongera kwanduzwa n'ibyo bice.
Mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi, gukaraba intoki bigamije gukuraho udukoko dutera indwara ("mikorobe") no kwirinda ko twanduzwa.
Ikinyamakuru cyitwa The New England Journal of Medicine kivuga ko mu bigo byinshi by'ubuvuzi, abantu benshi batigeze bakaraba intoki, ku buryo abaganga n'abaforomo benshi batigeze bakaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, bigatuma bakwirakwiza mikorobe.
Ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko gukaraba intoki neza n'ibindi bikorwa byoroheje bishobora kugabanya ku kigero cya 66 ku ijana ubwandu bw'amaraso bufitanye isano na catheter.
Inyandiko y'ubuyobozi ku isuku y'amaboko yatanzwe n'uyu muryango, ishobora kuboneka ku rubuga rwawo kugira ngo abantu bayisobanukirwe.
Hari inyandiko y'ingenzi yasuzumwe na Witby n'abandi.
Ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bishobora gupima no kwemeza isuku y'amaboko mu gihe ari ngombwa kugaragaza ko umuntu yubahiriza amategeko.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryashyizeho "ibihe bitanu" byo gukaraba intoki:
Nyuma yo guhura n'amaraso/imyanda yo mu mubiri
mbere yo gukora igikorwa cyo kwica udukoko, kandi
Nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi. Gukoresha imiti yo kugabanya ubukana bw'ubumara mu isabune ("imiti" cyangwa "antibacterial") bituma umuti wo gukaraba intoki ugira ubushobozi bwo kwica.
Kugira ngo umuntu 'akure' intoki ze mu gihe ari mu myanya y'umubiri cyangwa mu mimerere irimo abantu benshi batemera imiti, bishobora kuba byiza mbere yo kubagwa, cyangwa mu gihe ari mu mimerere irangwa n'imiti idakoresha imiti. Kugira ngo 'ukure' intoki zawe mu gihe ari mu myanya y'umubiri, ni ngombwa kugira akuma gashobora gukoreshwa no gufungwa udakoresheje intoki, kugira umuti wa chlorhexidine cyangwa uw'iyodiyine, kugira umufuka udakoresha imiti mu kumesa intoki nyuma yo kuzirya, n'ubushyo butakoresha imiti mu gusukura intoki n'ikindi gikoreshwa mu gusukura intoki.
Imyenda yose igomba kuvanwaho.
Ubusanzwe, iyo myitozo isaba ko umuntu akaraba intoki n'amavi mu gihe cy'iminota 2 - 6.
Nta mpamvu yo gukorakora igihe kirekire (iminota 10).
Mu gihe cyo gukaraba, amazi ku nkokora agomba kurindwa ngo atagaruka ku biganza.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, intoki ziruma n'igitambaro kitagira ubwandu kandi zikambikwa ikanzu y'ubuvuzi.
Kugira ngo udukoko dutera indwara tudahita twanduza abandi, ni byiza ko umuntu akaraba intoki cyangwa agakoresha umuti wo guhanagura intoki mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Ku bijyanye no kugenzura indwara z'ubwandu bw'ubwoko bwa staphylococcal mu bitaro, byaje kugaragara ko inyungu nini cyane mu gusukura intoki zivuye kuri 20% mbere yo gusukura, kandi ko inyungu nto cyane z'inyongera zatanzwe igihe ingano yo gusukura intoki yiyongereyeho 35% cyangwa irenga.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabune isanzwe, bigabanya inshuro zirenga eshatu ubwandu bw'indwara zandura ugereranyije no gukaraba n'isabune irwanya mikorobe. Kugereranya gukaraba intoki n'umuti urimo inzoga n'ukubika intoki n'isabune irwanya mikorobe mu gihe cy'iminota 30, byagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki n'inzoga bigabanya cyane guhumanya mikorobe ku kigero cya 26% ugereranyije n'isabune irwanya mikorobe.
Ariko, isabune n'amazi ni ingirakamaro cyane kurusha amavuta y'intoki akoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki mu gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'umwuka, mu kugabanya virusi ya H1N1 y'ibicurane bya A na Clostridium difficile. Mu mirimo yo kwita ku buzima, ingamba zo kunonosora isuku y'intoki zishobora kuba zikubiyemo kwigisha abakozi gukaraba intoki, kongera ibyangombwa by'amavuta akoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki, no kwibutsa abakozi mu buryo bwanditse no mu magambo.
Hakenewe ubushakashatsi bwimbitse ku birebana n'uburyo bwo kuvura bufite ingaruka nziza mu miryango itandukanye.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabune ni uburyo buhendutse, bw'ibanze bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza, ndetse no kugira imirire myiza.
Ariko kandi, kugira ngo abantu bashobore gukaraba intoki ku isi hose, ni ikibazo gikomeye bitewe no kubura amazi meza, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo zabo, mu mashuri no mu kazi.
Urugero, muri Afurika yo mu cyaro, ubwiherero bwa buri wese, bwaba ubw'ibanze cyangwa ubw'abaturage, bufite utuzu tworoheje two gukaraba intoki, n'ubwo hari uburyo bworoshye bwo kubaka aho bakaraza intoki.
Icyakora, kudahanagura intoki bishobora guterwa n'imyitwarire y'abantu aho guterwa no kubura isabune cyangwa amazi.
Gushishikariza abantu gukaraba intoki bakoresheje isabune no kubashyigikira bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro ifatwa mu rwego rw'amabwiriza, bikongera ubumenyi ku nyungu zo gukaraba intoki, kandi bigatuma habaho ihinduka ry'imyifatire y'abaturage mu gihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo ikore neza, ni ngombwa ko igenzura no kugenzura.
Isuzuma ry'ubushakashatsi 70 ryagaragaje ko uburyo bushingiye ku baturage ari bwo bw'ingirakamaro mu kongera gukaraba intoki mu bigo by'ubucuruzi by'abatuye mu karere, mu gihe gahunda zo gukwirakwiza ubutumwa ari zo zidakora neza. Urugero rwo gukangurira abantu gukaraba intoki mu mashuri ni "uburyo bw'inyenyeri eshatu" bwakozwe na UNICEF, bushishikariza amashuri gufata ingamba zoroshye, zidakomeye zo kwemeza ko abanyeshuri bakaraba intoki n'isabune, kimwe n'ibindi bikenewe mu isuku.
Iyo ibipimo by'ibanze byamaze kugerwaho, amashuri ashobora kujya mu byiciro by'inyenyeri kuva kuri imwe kugeza kuri eshatu.
Gushyiraho sitasiyo yo gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukangurira abantu gukaraba intoki bigamije kugabanya indwara n'urupfu rw'abana.
Umunsi Mpuzamahanga wo Gukaraba Intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bugamije kugerageza guhindura imyitwarire. Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus cya 2019-20, UNICEF yashishikarije abantu gukoresha imashini yo gukaraba intoki.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere ari byo bifite akamaro kanini mu kwirinda DALY.
Icyakora, hari isuzuma ryagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari byo by'ingenzi kurusha andi mahame yo kwiyeza no kwirinda indwara.
Akamaro ko gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu - cyane cyane ku bantu bafite ibibazo by'uburwayi, urugero nk'ababyeyi babyaye cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse bari mu bitaro - katangajwe bwa mbere mu kinyejana cya 19 n'abantu babiri bashyize imbere isuku y'intoki: umuganga w'Umuhungari witwa Ignaz Semmelweis wakoraga i Vienne muri Otirishiya, na Florence Nightingale, Umwongereza "washinze ubuforomo bugezweho".
Icyo gihe abantu benshi batekerezaga ko ubwandu bwagaragaye bitewe n'umwanda witwa miasmus.
Mu myaka ya za 80, icyorezo cy'imirire n'indwara ziterwa n'ubuzima, cyatumye ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, gikora cyane mu kongera isuku y'amaboko, nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu 2020 byatumye ibihugu byinshi byongera ubumenyi ku kamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu kwirinda indwara zandura nk'izi.
Urugero, mu Budage, ibishushanyo by'amafoto byerekana "uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki " byashyizwe hafi y'ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu mazu y'ibiro n'ahandi hantu bakoresha amazi mu bikoresho byo mu kirere.
Imvugo ngo "kwima ukuboko" isobanura ko umuntu atemeye ko hari icyo yakoze cyangwa ko hari icyo yakoze.
Iryo jambo rikomoka mu gice cya Matayo cyo muri Bibiliya aho Ponsiyo Pilato yafashe umwanzuro wo kwiyambura Yesu Kristo, ariko ryakomeje kuba imvugo ikoreshwa cyane mu moko amwe n'amwe y'icyongereza.
Muri Shakespeare, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'agahato mu rwego rwo kwihana ikizinga cy'igitekerezo kigaragaza umutimanama we w'icyaha ku byaha yakoze no kuba yarashishikarije umugabo we gukora ibyaha.
Nanone kandi, byagaragaye ko abantu bakunze gukaraba intoki kurusha abandi, nyuma yo kwibuka cyangwa gutekereza ku bikorwa by'ubwiyandarike, kandi ko baha agaciro cyane ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki.
Byongeye kandi, abantu bemerewe gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gutekereza muri ubwo buryo, ntibashobora gukora indi mirimo yo "kubanza gukora isuku" nk'ibikorwa by'ubwitange.
Amadini atanga inama yo gukaraba intoki haba mu rwego rw'isuku no mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo. Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo n'amazi y'isabune nta bikoresho byo gukaraba intoki ni kimwe mu bikorwa byo gukaraba intoki bivugwa mu madini menshi, harimo idini rya Baha'i, idini ry'Abahindu, idini rya Kiyahudi rivuga ko umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'umuhango, muri Tevila na Netilat Yedyim, mu Bukristo rivuga ko umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'igitangaza, no muri Islamu rivuga ko umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo kugira ngo abone isuku nyuma yo gukora ibikorwa runaka.
Mu idini ry'Abahindu, Abayahudi n'Abayisilamu, gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero ni itegeko.
Kandi, mu idini ry'Abahindu, iry'Ababuda, iry'Abasiki, iry'Abayahudi n'iry'Abisilamu, gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma y'ifunguro ryose ni itegeko.
Gucunga ibyago byo gukwirakwiza COVID-19 mu kazi
Gukora mu kazi ni uburyo bwo gukemura ibibazo byugarije umutekano n'ubuzima, mu rwego rwo kwirinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), mu rwego rwo kwirinda icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu kazi.
Ingaruka z'ubwandu bw'indwara mu kazi zifite aho zihuriye n'aho umuntu akorera ndetse n'akazi akora, hashingiwe ku bipimo by'ibyago by'ibanze by'ubwandu, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage, n'impamvu z'ibyago ku bakozi bafite ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'ubuyobozi bw'ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi muri Amerika (OSHA), akazi gafite ibyago by'ubushyamirane buke ni akazi gafite ubukana ku bantu n'abandi bakozi, aho ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zirimo: gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gukurikiza amabwiriza yo guhumeka, no gusukura no guhanagura ibidukikije by'akazi buri gihe.
Ibikorwa byo guhura n'abantu bafite ibyago byo kudahura na bo ni ibyo bisaba guhura kenshi cyangwa bya hafi n'abantu batazi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba banduye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba baranduye bitewe no gukwirakwiza mu baturage cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Muri ibyo hakubiyemo abakozi bakorana n'abaturage muri rusange, urugero nk'amashuri, ahantu hakorera abantu benshi, n'ibigo bimwe na bimwe bigurisha ibintu byinshi.
Uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura, ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago kuri uyu muryango zirimo: guhanahana amakuru n'ibisukure by'umwuka bikora neza, gukoresha indorerwamo, no gukomeza kubona ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite mu gihe umuntu wahuye na COVID-19 yaba afite.
OSHA isanga abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubuzima n'abakora mu nzu y'ubuvuzi bafite ibyago byo guhura n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 cyangwa ukekwaho ubwandu, kandi ibi bishobora kongera ibyago byo guhura n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 cyangwa ukekwaho ubwandu mu gihe abakozi bakora, cyangwa bakusanya cyangwa bagakora ibipimo by'umuntu ufite COVID-19 cyangwa ukekwaho ubwandu.
Mu byuma bibangamiye abo bakozi harimo ibyuma bibangamiye ingufu z'ubwubatsi, urugero nk'ibyuma bibangamira ingufu z'ubushyuhe, n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku kazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi mu kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba batarahagera bitewe n'uburwayi, kuba bagomba kwita ku bandi cyangwa gutinya ko bashobora guhura n'abandi.
Ibicuruzwa bikenewe, n'uburyo bwo kubikenera (nk'igihe bibaye bike cyangwa kugura binyuze mu gutanga cyangwa mu gutembera), bishobora guhindura imiterere y'ubucuruzi.
Amaherezo, urujya n'uruza rw'ibintu mu turere twibasiwe cyane na COVID-19 rushobora kugira ingaruka. Gutegura no gutegura ibisubizo ku ndwara zandura bishobora gukoreshwa mu kuyobora ibikorwa by'ubwirinzi.
Gahunda zireba ibyiciro by'ibyago bifitanye isano n'aho bakorera ndetse n'imirimo bakora, harimo aho byaturuka, ibyago bituruka mu ngo no mu miryango, n'ibyago by'abakozi ku giti cyabo, nk'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara z'indwara zidakira.
Nanone kandi, bagaragaza uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyago bishobora guterwa n'uko habaye icyorezo, n'uburyo bwo kwirinda ibyago bishobora guterwa n'icyo cyorezo.
Gutegura no gusubiza indwara zandura bishobora gushingira ku nama z'igihugu cyangwa iz'igihugu.
Intego zo gusubiza icyorezo zirimo: kugabanya ikwirakwira hagati y'abakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'ibibazo by'ubuzima, kubungabunga ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku zindi nzego mu muyoboro w'ibicuruzwa byabo.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage aho ikorerwa bufite ingaruka ku bisubizo bifatwa.
Urutonde rw'ibyangombwa by'ibyago ni igishushanyo gikoreshwa cyane mu rwego rwo gushyira hamwe ibyangombwa by'ibyago hakurikijwe uko bikora mu buzima n'umutekano mu kazi.
Aho COVID-19 idashobora gukurwaho, ingamba z'ubuhanga ni zo z'ingenzi cyane, zikurikirwa n'ingamba z'ubuyobozi, hanyuma hakagira ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite.
Igenzura ryubwubatsi ririmo gutandukanya abakozi n'akaga gakomoka ku kazi, hatitawe ku myitwarire y'abakozi, kandi rishobora kuba igisubizo cyoroshye cyane mu gushyira mu bikorwa.
Ubuyobozi ni ihinduka mu miyoborere cyangwa imikorere y'akazi, bisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite (PPE) bifatwa nk'ibidashobora gukora neza kurusha inzego z'ubwubatsi n'iz'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu gukumira imibonano imwe n'imwe.
PPE zose zigomba gutoranywa ku giti cy'ibyago ku bakozi, zikagenerwa mu buryo bukwiriye (urugero, imashini z'ubuhumekero), zikambara buri gihe kandi neza, zigenzurwa buri gihe, zigakorwaho imirimo kandi zigasimbuzwa igihe bikenewe, kandi zikurwaho neza, zigatunganywa neza cyangwa zigashyirwamo kugira ngo zirinde kwanduzwa.
Dukurikije Itegeko ry'Ubutegetsi bw'Ubuzima n'Umutekano mu Mirimo (OSHA), imirimo ifite ibyago bike byo guhura n'abantu, ni ukuvuga guhura by'umurimo n'abandi bakozi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zisabwa ku kazi kose zirimo: gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi neza, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kurinda abantu guhumeka, gutwika no kwitsamura, gutanga amasahani n'ibikoresho by'imyanda, gutegura imyenda ya kure cyangwa ihurije hamwe niba ari ngombwa, kubuza abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no gusukura no guhanagura ibidukikije by'akazi buri gihe.
Gushyiraho uburyo bwo kumenya no gutandukanya abantu bashobora kuba banduye mu kazi ni intambwe ikomeye mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi.
Ikigo cya Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga inama ko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ifata imyakura (Acute Respiratory Disease) baguma mu rugo igihe cyose bamaze nibura amasaha 24 badafite umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro, cyangwa indi ndwara iyo ari yo yose, badafite imiti igabanya umuriro cyangwa indi miti ihindura ibimenyetso, kandi ko hari politiki z'ikiruhuko ziyoroshya zemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo bitabe ku muntu wo mu muryango urwaye, kandi ko abakozi bamenya neza izo ngamba.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, ibikorwa bifite ibyago byo guhura n'abantu bake ni ibikorwa bisaba ko umuntu ahura kenshi cyangwa hafi cyane n'abantu bari mu birometero bitandatu (1.8 m) batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba banduye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba banduye SARS-CoV-2 bitewe n'uko hashobora kuba hari ikwirakwira ry'abantu benshi mu gace k'akazi, cyangwa se kubera ko umuntu aherutse gukora urugendo mpuzamahanga mu gace karimo ikwirakwira ry'abantu benshi banduye COVID-19.
Muri byo harimo abakozi bafite umubano usesuye n'abaturage basanzwe nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorerwamo ibikorwa by'abaturage benshi, hamwe na gahunda zimwe na zimwe z'ubucuruzi buciriritse. Gushiraho ibishushanyo mbonera by'umwuka mu byuma by'ubwubatsi mu bigo by'ubwubatsi bigenewe aya matsinda y'abanduye, kongera ibipimo by'ubwandu, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nk'ibikoresho bya plastiki bisukuye, no gushyiraho amadirishya yo gutwara ku bakiriya. Gushyiraho abakozi mu bigo by'ubuyobozi bigenzura abarwayi mu nzu, guhindura inama za buri wese ku giti cye mu buryo bwo gutumanaho, gushyiraho imbonerahamwe, kwirinda ingendo zitari ngombwa ku bakiriya ku bibanza birimo COVID-19, guteza imbere gahunda z'ibyago, harimo: gushyiraho urubuga rwo gukemura ibibazo by'abakozi bakoresha imyenda yo kumesa, gutanga abakozi bahawe amahugurwa ku bijyanye n'imikorere ya COVID-19, no gushishikariza abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi n'ubushakashatsi ku buryo bwo kwirinda COVID-19, harimo kwambara udupfukamunwa cyangwa ibindi bikoresho by'ibanga bikingira umutekano, no kugabanya ibyago byo gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubwoko.
Abagize iri tsinda ry'ibyago bakenera gukoresha imashini zo guhumeka gake cyane.
Iyo umuntu arwaye mu ndege, ingamba zikwiye zo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bantu bari mu ndege zirimo: gusiga umuntu urwaye ku birometero 6 uvuye ku bandi, gushyiraho umukozi w'abagenzi wo kwita ku muntu urwaye no guha umuntu urwaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumusaba ko yambara umwenda wo mu kanwa no mu mazuru mu gihe yitsamuye cyangwa asese.
Abagenzi barwaye cyangwa abakora ku bikoresho by'umubiri cyangwa ahantu hashobora guhumanya umubiri, bagomba kwambara udushumi tw'ubuvuzi dushobora gukoreshwa, kandi niba umukozi urwaye afite umuriro, agasonza kenshi, cyangwa afite ubumuga bwo guhumeka, ashobora kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi by'umuntu ku giti cye.
Inkweto n'ibindi bikoresho bigomba kujugunywa mu mufuka ufite ubukana, kandi imiterere yahumanyijwe igomba guhanagurwa no gukingirwa nyuma. Ku bwato bw'ubucuruzi, harimo ubwato bw'ubwato bw'ubwato n'ubundi bwato bw'abashyitsi, mu kugenzura ibyago harimo guhagarika urugendo iyo umuntu arwaye no kwisanzura no guhita amenyesha ikigo nderabuzima cyo mu bwato niba umuntu arwaye cyangwa indi ndwara mu gihe ari mu bwato.
Mu buryo bwiza, gukurikirana kwa muganga bigomba gukorwa mu cyumba cy'umuntu waciwe. Ku mashuri n'ibigo byita ku bana, CDC isaba ko hashyirwaho igihe gito cyo gusukura cyangwa gusubizaho indwara mu gihe umuntu wafashwe n'iyo ndwara yaba yaramaze igihe mu kigo cy'ishuri kitagira ikwirakwira mu muryango.
Iyo hari ikwirakwira ryoroheje kugeza ku ryoroheje ry'abaturage, ingamba zo gutandukanya abantu zishobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa, nko guhagarika amafunguro mu ngendo zo mu karere, mu makoraniro no mu bindi biganiro binini, nko mu mashuri y'imyitozo ngororamubiri cyangwa mu masomo yo kuririmba cyangwa muri resitora, kongera intera hagati y'amadesika, guhuza igihe cyo kugera n'igihe cyo kuruhuka, kugabanya abasura bitari ngombwa, no gukoresha ahantu hitandukanye ho mu biro by'ubuzima ku bana bafite ibimenyetso nk'iby'ibicurane.
Mu gihe hari ikwirakwira rikwiye mu baturage, birashoboka ko hashyirwaho ibiruhuko by'amashuri byongerewe, uretse ingamba zo kwirinda. Ku bakozi bashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bakora ibikorwa bya buri munsi, ibyago by'ubuzima bwihuse bifatwa nk'ibito na CDC.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bagomba guhura n'abantu bemejwe cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, basabwa gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ay'abaganga b'ubutabazi b'ibihe byihutirwa, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'umuntu ku giti cye.
Niba hari aho umuntu yahuye cyane mu gihe cyo gufata, abakozi bagomba gusukura no gutunganya udusimba tw'akazi n'ibikoresho byabo, bakoresheje imashini yo gusukura mu rugo cyangwa imyenda mbere yo kubikoresha, kandi bagakurikiza amabwiriza y'imikorere asanzwe yo kubika no kujugunya ibikoresho bya PPE byakoreshejwe no kubika no kumesa imyenda.
OSHA isuzuma ko bamwe mu bakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima n'abakora mu nzu y'ubuvuzi bari mu byiciro by'ibyago byo guhura n'abantu benshi cyangwa se by'ibigo by'ubuvuzi.
Ibikorwa byibasira cyane harimo gutanga ubuvuzi, gufasha, gukora ibizamini no gutwara abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho.
Izo ndwara ziba ziteje akaga gakomeye cyane iyo abakozi bakoreye cyangwa bakoramo ibipimo by'abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19 batanga imiti ituma habaho Aerosol.
Imikorere ituma habaho aerosol ikubiyemo gutwara umugozi, gukoresha imashini ituma umuntu aba mu mazi, gukoresha bronchoscopy, gukoresha imyenda imwe n'imwe cyangwa gukoresha ibipimo by'imikorere.
Ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi by'abafite ibyago byo guhura n'abantu benshi bikubiyemo abantu bategura imibiri y'abantu bafite COVID-19 bizwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bayirwaye igihe bapfuye; iyo bakoze ibizamini by'ubuvuzi, baba bafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura na bo. Ibindi byunganizi by'izi tsinda ry'ibyago birimo ibyumba by'ubwirinzi ku barwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19, harimo no gukora imikorere ikora aerosol.
Mu mirimo imwe n'imwe y'ubuvuzi no mu mirimo y'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwihariye bwo guhanahana ibihaha bishobora kuba bikwiriye.
Ibipimo bigomba gufatwa mu buryo buhuje n'ingamba zo kurinda ubuzima bw'abantu.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye ko abarwayi baza, bakurikije niba ari abarwayi bakekwaho COVID-19, bakurwa mu byumba by'abarwayi. Uretse ibindi bikoresho bya PPE, OSHA yasabye ko abantu bakora mu kirere kiri hafi y'ibirenge 6 by'abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kwandura SARS-CoV-2, n'abakora imikorere ikora aerosol, bakurwa mu byumba by'abarwayi.
Muri Amerika, NIOSH yemeje N95 filtration facepiece respirators cyangwa zirenzeho zigomba gukoreshwa mu rwego rw'ingamba z'ubwirinzi bw'ubuhumekero mu buryo bwimbitse, bwanditse, harimo gupima ubwiza, amahugurwa n'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi.
Ubundi bwoko bw'ibikoresho byo guhumeka bushobora gutanga uburinzi bwinshi no kunoza ihumure ry'abakozi. WHO ntishyigikira ko abantu bahumeka kubera ko COVID-19 ari indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, aho kuba ishobora gukwirakwizwa binyuze mu mazi yo mu mubiri.
OMS isaba ko ku bantu bakora ibizamini ku kiraro, hakoreshwa agapfukamunwa kamwe gusa.
Ku bantu bakusanya, bita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bafite uburyo butera ubukana bwa aerosol cyangwa bakabatwara, WHO irasaba ko bakoresha agapfukamunwa, indorerwamo, n'utugati.
Iyo habaye igikorwa cyo gukora aerosol, agapfukamunwa kabaga gashyirwa mu cyuma cyo guhumeka cya N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Mu gihe urwego rw'ubuzima rw'isi rwemeza ko gutanga PPE ku isi hose bidakwiriye, WHO irasaba ko hakorwa Telemedicine, ko hakorwa ingamba zo kugabanya ibyangombwa bya PPE nko kuba hari udukingirizo tw'ibanga, nko kuba abantu bafasha umuntu wafashwe na COVID-19 ari bo bonyine bemerewe kwinjira mu cyumba, gukoresha PPE ikenewe gusa mu kazi runaka, gukoresha imashini imwe yo guhumeka ntawe ugiye kuyikura mu gihe yita ku barwayi benshi bafite icyorezo kimwe, kugenzura no guhuza urubuga rw'itangwa rya PPE, no guhangana n'abantu batagira ubwandu bakoresha udupfukamunwa.
