Catherine, CRT (Amanda K, Amy V, Brian J, Doreen D, Gregory V, Jamie V, Joel L, Lynette L, Ryan M, na Tony S), n'abandi bagize itsinda ry'abayobozi (Grant I, Heather W, Jamie V, Jennienne U, Lisa S, Robin A, Ryan M, na Toby N).
Angiotensin - converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni ingirabuzimafatizo ifitanye isano n'uruhu rw'inyuma rw'ingirabuzimafatizo (ingingo z'ingirabuzimafatizo) mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu bihimba by'umura, no mu maraso.
ACE2 iguza imikorere ya angiotensin-modifying enzyme (ACE) ifitanye isano no kugabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II no kuzamura angiotensin (1-7), bigatuma iba ikibanza cy'ubuvuzi cyizewe mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora kandi nk'aho ariho ingirabuzimafatizo yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za coronavirusi zimwe na zimwe.
Ubuhinduzi bwa enzyme mu bantu bukunze kwitwa hACE2.
Angiotensin - modifying enzyme 2 ni metaloenzime irimo zinki iba mu bice by'imbere mu mubiri no ku bindi bice by'umubiri.
ACE2 igizwe n'urubuga rwa N-terminal peptidase M2 n'urubuga rwa C-terminal collectrin cyclic amino acid.
ACE2 ni poroteyine yo mu bwoko bwa I ifite uruhu rw'umwimerere, ifite uruhu rw'umwimerere rufite uruhu rw'umwimerere rwihariye ku mubiri, mu bihaha no mu bindi binyabuzima.
Urubuga rwo hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo ya ACE2 runyurwamo n'undi musemburo witwa Shadese, maze poroteyine ihumeka ikava mu maraso ikajya mu cyondo.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifitanye isano cyane cyane n'uruhu rw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso z'ubwoko bwa II, intaro nto, insoro n'imitsi y'amaraso, n'ingingo z'amaraso z'imitsi y'amaraso.
ACE2 mRNA iboneka no mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko n'icy'ubwonko.
Umurimo w'ibanze wa ACE2 ni ugukora nk'umuvuduko wa ACE.
ACE isenya ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin I mu buryo bw'ibinyabutabire, ikavamo ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin II.
ACE2 isenya amino acide ya carboxyl-terminal phenylalanine ivuye muri angiotensin II (Asp - Arg - Val - Tyr - Ile - His - Pro - Phe) ikayisenya mu mazi ikavamo angiotensin (1 - 7), (H - Asp - Arg - Tyr - Ile - His - Pro - OH).
ACE2 [des-Arg9] ishobora no gusenya indi peptides nyinshi harimo bradykinin, epelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi igenzura gutwara mu ruhu imikorere y'indwara ya SLC6A19, kandi byerekanwa ko igira uruhare mu ndwara y'umutima.
Nk'umushongi w'umushongi, ukora nk'aho ariho ha mbere hajya mu ngirabuzimafatizo za coronavirusi zimwe na zimwe, harimo ACE2, HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, konti S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 ifatanye na ACE2 ku gice cya enzymatic ku gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo, bituma habaho endositosis no kwimura virusi na enzymes byombi mu gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo kiri mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Iyi nzira yo kwinjira kandi isaba ko poroteyine ya S itunganywa n'umuti wa serine protease TMPRSS2, ubufasha bwo kuyihagarika ni bwo bugikomeje gushakishwa nk'umuti ushobora kuvura. Ibyo byatumye bamwe batekereza ko kugabanya urugero rwa ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo bishobora gufasha kurwanya ubwandu.
Icyakora, inzego nyinshi z'ubuvuzi n'iz'ubuyobozi zasabye ko imiti isanzwe ya ACE inhibitors na ARB ikomeza gukoreshwa.
Isuzuma ryakozwe mu buryo buhuje n'imikorere n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, ryagaragaje ko "gukoresha ACE inhibitors byari bifitanye isano n'igabanuka rikomeye ry'ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'ibicurane ku kigero cya 34 ku ijana ugereranyije n'ibyangombwa".
Nanone kandi, "abafashwe na ACE inhibitors bari bafite ibyago bike byo kurwara pneumonia, cyane cyane abafite uburwayi bwo mu mutwe n'uburwayi bwo mu mutima.
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors byari bifitanye isano no kugabanya impfu ziterwa na pneumonia, nubwo ingaruka zari nke ugereranyije n'ingaruka z'uburwayi bwa pneumonia muri rusange".
Igisukurwa cy'umuntu ACE2 (rhACE2) ni umuti mushya wo kuvura indwara z'ubuhumekero, kandi byagaragaye ko bifasha mu kuvura imikorere y'amaraso n'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu ngurube z'abana bafite indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'ubuhumekero bw'ubuhumekero buturutse ku mikorobe.
Mu muntu, iherezo ry'ubuzima bwa rhACE2 ni amasaha agera ku 10 n'umunsi w'ibikorwa ni iminota 30, n'igihe cy'ibikorwa ni amasaha 24.
Bimwe mu byatahuwe bigaragaza ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti wizewe ku bantu batagaragaza ubukana mu ndwara ziterwa n'ubukana bw'imiti yitwa Renin-angiotensin system inhibitors (RAS inhibitors) cyangwa indwara ziterwa n'ubwiyongere bw'imiti yitwa angiotensin II.
COVID-19 Apps ni porogaramu za porogaramu zigendanwa zashyizweho mu rwego rwo gufasha mu buryo bwo gukurikirana abantu, ni ukuvuga uburyo bwo kumenya abantu ("abavugana") bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu wanduye, mu gisubizo cy'icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20.
Mu turere tumwe na tumwe n'ubutegetsi bumwe na bumwe, hari porogaramu nyinshi zatangijwe cyangwa zashyizweho, zifashishijwe na leta.
Hari uburyo bwinshi bwo gukora porogaramu zo gushakisha abantu.
Hari impungenge z'ibanga zagiye zivugwa, cyane cyane ku bihereranye n'uburyo bwo gukurikirana imimerere y'abahakoresha porogaramu.
Uburyo budafite ubushishozi burimo gukoresha Bluetooth kugira ngo umuntu ashobore kubona aho ari hafi ya telefoni ye.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byombi byatangaje ko bizashyira hamwe imikorere yo gushyigikira porogaramu nk'izi za Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu zayo za Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa yashyizeho porogaramu ikorana na Alipay, ituma abaturage bashobora kureba niba bagiranye imishyikirano n'abantu bafite COVID-19.
Ubu ikoreshwa mu migi isaga 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapuru, ikoreshwa na porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango wa IT wo mu karere, yasohotse nk'umushinga wa Open Source, kandi izahabwa leta. Macedonia ya Ruguru yatangije porogaramu ya "StopKorona!" ishingiye kuri Bluetooth, igamije kumenya abantu bashobora kuba barwaye, no guha inzego z'ubuzima ibisubizo byihuse.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itangazamakuru n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Mata 2020, iyi porogaramu yari itegereje kwemerwa na Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yavuze ko porogaramu yo gushakisha abantu yari mu cyiciro cyateye imbere, kandi ko izaboneka mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'iyi ("StopCovid") na yo yari yarateganyijwe muri Ireland no mu Bufaransa.
Australia na New Zealand byombi birimo gusuzuma porogaramu zishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether na BlueTrace ya Singapore. Uburusiya bushaka gutangiza porogaramu ya geofencing ku barwayi basanganywe COVID-19 baba i Moscou, igamije kwemeza ko batagomba kuva mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu muri kaminuza ya Cambridge wigisha iby'ubwubatsi mu by'umutekano, yavuze ibibazo byinshi bishobora kuvuka mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga, harimo ibibazo by'ibinyoma n'ibishobora kubura umusaruro mu gihe porogaramu ikoreshwa n'abantu bake.
Mu gukemura impungenge ku gukwirakwira kwa porogaramu za "coronavirus" zishobora kuyobya cyangwa kwangiza, Apple yagennye ubwoko bw'imiryango ishobora gushyiramo porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus mububiko bwayo bwa App Store, ikabishyira mu bigo "byemewe" gusa cyangwa byemewe.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho ingamba nk'izo.
Abashyigikiye ubwirinzi bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka zo kugenzura ku bwinshi hakoreshejwe porogaramu za coronavirus, by'umwihariko niba ibikorwa remezo by'ubugenzuzi byubatswe mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus bizasenywa nyuma y'uko iki cyorezo kirangiye.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe asaga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko hashyirwaho imipaka ku buryo bwo kugenzura.
Amashyirahamwe yatangaje ibintu umunani ku mishinga ya leta:
igenzura rigomba kuba "ryemewe, rikenewe kandi rifite igipimo cyaryo";
hagomba kuba hari ingingo isoza ibisobanuro by'ubugenzuzi n'ubugenzuzi;
Gukoresha amakuru bigomba kuba byuzuye ku mpamvu za COVID-19.
Umutekano n'ubwirenga by'amakuru bigomba kurindwa kandi bigaragarira mu bimenyetso;
Igenzura ry'ikoranabuhanga rigomba kwirinda gushishikariza ivangura no gutesha agaciro uburenganzira bw'umuntu;
Uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo gusangira amakuru n'abantu ba gatatu bugomba gusobanurwa mu mategeko;
Hakwiye gushyirwaho ingamba zo kurinda uburenganzira bw'abaturage mu kurwanya no kurwanya ihohoterwa;
"Kwifatanya mu buryo bufite ireme" bizakenerwa n "abafite uruhare bose", harimo impuguke mu by'ubuzima rusange n'amatsinda adafite uburenganzira. The German Chaos Computer Club (CCC) na Reporters Without Borders (RSF) na zo zatangaje urutonde rw'ibanze.
Gahunda ya Google / Apple igamije gukemura ikibazo cyo kugenzura buri gihe, mu gukura uburyo bwo gukurikirana muburyo bwa sisitemu y'imikorere y'ibikoresho byabo iyo bidakenewe.
Ibihugu bimwe byakoresheje uburyo bwo gukurikirana ahantu hashingiye ku muyoboro aho gukoresha porogaramu, bikuraho icyifuzo cyo gukuramo porogaramu no kwirinda gukurikirana.
Muri Isirayeli, uburyo bwo gukurikirana abantu hakoreshejwe imiyoboro bwemewe.
Ibisubizo bishingiye ku muyoboro bifite uburyo bwo kubona amakuru y'ahantu hakoreshejwe imashini, bishobora kugira ibibazo by'ibanga by'ibanga.
Icyakora, ntabwo sisitemu zose zifite seriveri nkuru zikeneye kwiga amakuru yerekeye ahantu umuntu ari; hari sisitemu nyinshi zishinzwe kurinda ubuzima bwite zashyizweho zikoresha seriveri nkuru gusa kugirango ziganire (reba igice kiri hasi).
Sisitemu idakoresha porogaramu yakoreshejwe mu gukurikirana abo bahuye na bo muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, sisitemu yakusanyije amakuru yo gukurikirana aturuka ku masoko atandukanye, harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana igikoresho cya terefone n'amakuru y'ubucuruzi bw'ikarita, maze ibi bifatanya mu gutanga amakuru binyuze mu butumwa bw'umwandiko ku bantu bashobora kuba barwaye.
Usibye gukoresha aya makuru kugira ngo abantu bashobora guhura na yo bamenyekane, leta yashyize ahagaragara amakuru yerekeye aho umuntu ari kubera impinduka z'ingenzi mu mategeko agenga ubuzima bwite bw'amakuru, nyuma y'icyorezo cya MERS cyabaye muri icyo gihugu.
Aya makuru aboneka ku buntu binyuze kuri porogaramu nyinshi na za interineti. Ibihugu byinshi, harimo n'u Budage, byatekereje gukoresha uburyo bwa centralized no kurinda ubuzima bwite.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 6 Mata 2020, ayo makuru yari atarakurwaho.
Kubona amakuru ku byerekeye ubuzima bwite ni igitekerezo cyamaze igihe kirekire, gifite ibitabo byinshi by'ubushakashatsi kuva nibura mu 2013. Kugeza ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'inzobere asaga icumi yari arimo akora ku bisubizo by'ibanga, nko gukoresha Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) kugira ngo umuntu ashobore kubona amakuru ku buryo buhamye ku bindi bikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga.
Ariko kandi, PEPP-PT ni uburyo bwo guhuza bufite uburyo bw'uburyo bw'icyicaro gikuru n'ubw'icyicaro gikuru, kandi ntabwo ari porotokaramu imwe. Porotokaramu z'icicicaro gikuru zirimo ikoranabuhanga ry'icyakwirakwizwa ry'ibanga-kuburinda (DP-PPT/DP-3T), nomero z'ubutabazi z'agateganyo (TCN, mbere z'umubare w'ibihe by'ubutabazi, CEN), porotokaramu z'ibanga z'ibanga n'uburyo bwo gushakisha amakuru y'ibanga (PACT) n'ibindi.
