Urukingo rwa COVID-19 ni urukingo rwibumbatiwe rwo kurinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Nubwo nta rukingo na rumwe rwarangije ibizamini byo kuvura, hari byinshi bikorwa mu rwego rwo gukora urukingo nk'urwo.
Mu mpera za Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryavuze ko ritazigera ritegereza ko urukingo rwo kurinda SARS-CoV-2, virusi iteza indwara, ruzaboneka mu gihe kitarenze amezi 18.
Abakandida batanu b'inkingo bari mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi bw'umutekano mu kwezi kwa kane.
COVID-19 yamenyekanye mu Ukuboza 2019.
Mu 2020 habaye icyorezo gikomeye ku isi, cyatumye hashyirwaho imbaraga nyinshi mu bushakashatsi no mu gukora inkingo.
Imiryango myinshi ikoresha genomes zasohotse mu gukora inkingo zishobora kurinda SARS-CoV-2.
Mu kwezi kwa Mata, byatangajwe ko ingamba za CEPI mu iterambere ry'urukingo ari umuvuduko, ubushobozi bwo gukora, igenamigambi ry'ibipimo n'ubuhanga ku isi hose.
Muri Mata, abahanga mu bya siyansi ba CEPI batangaje ko mu ntangiriro za 2020, hari imbuga 10 zitandukanye zikoranabuhanga zari ziri mu bushakashatsi n'iterambere mu rwego rwo gukora urukingo rw'ubwirinzi bw'indwara ya COVID-19.
Intego z'ibanze z'urubuga mu byiciro bya mbere by'ubushakashatsi ku mutekano zirimo:
Amoko ya nucleic (DNA na RNA) (umuvugizi w'icyiciro cya mbere n'umukandida w'urukingo: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
Virusi (icyiciro cya mbere cy'abashakashatsi n'abakandida b'urukingo: CanSino Biologics, adenovirus type 5 vector)
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'abahanga muri CEPI muri Mata, abashaka urukingo 115 bari mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'iterambere, 78 muri bo bakaba baremejwe nk'imishinga ikora (nk'uko bivugwa na Milken Institute), naho abandi 37 batangajwe, ariko amakuru make y'abaturage araboneka (arimo gukorwa cyangwa ateganijwe).
Icyiciro cya I-II cy'igerageza kigizwe n'ibizamini by'ibanze by'umutekano n'ubwirinzi, akenshi bikorerwa mu buryo bw'amahirwe, mu buryo bufite placebo-bugenzurwa kandi mu bice byinshi, bigatuma dosiye iba ari nziza cyane.
Ibizamini by'icyiciro cya III bikunze kuba bikubiyemo abantu benshi, harimo itsinda ry'abategetsi rigenzura ingaruka mbi ku gipimo cyiza, n'ikigeragezo cyo kureba niba urukingo rukora neza mu gukumira indwara.
Mu bakandida 79 b'urukingo bari mu bikorwa by'iterambere (byemejwe mu ntangiriro za Mata 2020), 74 ntibari bakiri mu igeragezwa ry'abantu (bari bakiri mu bushakashatsi "mbere ya gahunda yo gupima indwara").
