Umusaruro w'amaraso y'abavuwe, arimo ibice by'amaraso by'abakize kandi afite ubushobozi bwihariye bwo kwirinda iyi virusi, ushobora kwiyongera kugira ngo utegure vuba.
Indwara ya Koronavirusi, itsinda ry'indwara ziterwa no kugirana imishyikirano ya bugufi
Li Wenliang, umuganga mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan, yanduye COVID-19 nyuma yo gukangurira abantu gukwirakwiza virusi, arapfa.
